    [ServiceFaultID]   INT            IDENTITY (1, 1) NOT NULL,
    [ParentID]         INT            NOT NULL,
    [ParentType]       VARCHAR (300)  NULL,
    [ErrorMessage]     VARCHAR (8000) NULL,
    [ExceptionClass]   VARCHAR (8000) NULL,
    [FaultCode]        VARCHAR (8000) NULL,
    [FaultSubCode]     VARCHAR (8000) NULL,
    [FaultTimestamp]   DATETIME       NOT NULL,
    [Originator]       VARCHAR (8000) NULL,
    [StacktraceString] VARCHAR (8000) NULL,
    [Deleted]          TINYINT        DEFAULT ((0)) NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([ServiceFaultID] ASC)
);

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[orn_kex_LandingZone_WebAdverts] (
    [WebAdvertsID] INT          IDENTITY (1, 1) NOT NULL,
    [GUID]         VARCHAR (38) NULL,
    [Deleted]      TINYINT      DEFAULT ((0)) NULL,
    [Created]      DATETIME     DEFAULT (getdate()) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [KEX_LZ_WebAdverts] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([WebAdvertsID] ASC)
);



===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz
AS
SELECT fs.* FROM 
(SELECT MAX(Msk_kex_felvstatuszID) AS MAXFelvastatuszID, Idjelentkezo AS Idjelentkezo FROM dbo.msk_kex_felvstatusz
WHERE Deleted=0
GROUP BY Idjelentkezo) a
INNER JOIN dbo.msk_kex_felvstatusz fs ON fs.Msk_kex_felvstatuszID=a.MAXFelvastatuszID

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_allasajanlatok_alap.sql =====


/*
M�dos�t�s:
    - 2022.11.28 T�th L�szl�
        - A dbo.People t�bla k�t�s m�dos�t�sa
*/
CREATE VIEW [dbo].[msk_kex_allasajanlatok_alap]
AS
    SELECT [A].[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID]
         , [A].[uzletag]
         , [A].[reszleg]
         , [A].[targy]
         , [A].[munkavegzes_helye]
         , [A].[datum_lejarat]
         , [A].[toborzo_info]
         , [P].[Name]
         , [P].[Mobile]
         , [A].[idmunkaltato]
         , [A].[idvezeto]
         , [A].[idtoborzo1]
         , [A].[idtoborzo2]
         , [A].[idceg]
         , [MKL].[Indokok]
         , [A].[datum_lezaras]
         , [A].[link]
    FROM [dbo].[msk_kex_allasajanlatok] [A]
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[People] [P] ON [P].[PERNR] = [A].[toborzo_torzsszam] AND [P].[Deleted] = 0
        LEFT OUTER JOIN [dbo].[msk_kex_lezarasindokok] [MKL] ON [A].[Idlezarasindok] = [MKL].[Msk_kex_lezarasindokokID]
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_JelentkezoBelepes.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_JelentkezoBelepes
AS
SELECT        j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID, fv.Belepesdatum
FROM          dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz AS fv
            INNER JOIN dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS j ON fv.Idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID



===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_map_riport.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_map_riport
AS
SELECT        J.msk_kex_jelentkezokID, J.datum, J.hp_nev, J.ajanlo_nev, A.targy, J.nev, F.LookupValue AS felveve, B.Ddatum AS ujfelveteldatum, A.idceg, A.reszleg, A.munkavegzes_helye, A.idvezeto, A.idtoborzo1, A.idtoborzo2, 
                         J.idallasajanlat, p2.Name AS toborzo_name2, p1.Name AS toborzo_name1, J.map_beerkezes, m.LookupValue AS map_dokumentacionev
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS J LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz AS fs ON fs.Idjelentkezo = J.msk_kex_jelentkezokID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_LookupList AS F ON F.LookupListID = fs.Idfelvstatusz LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_LookupList AS m ON J.idmap_dokumentacio = m.LookupListID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok AS A ON J.idallasajanlat = A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.People AS p1 ON A.idtoborzo1 = p1.PeopleID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.People AS p2 ON p2.PeopleID = A.idtoborzo2 LEFT JOIN
                             (SELECT        Idjelentkezo, CASE idfelvstatusz WHEN 6 THEN Belepesdatum ELSE NULL END AS Ddatum
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz
                               WHERE        (Msk_kex_felvstatuszID IN
                                                             (SELECT        MAX(Msk_kex_felvstatuszID) AS ID
                                                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz AS msk_kex_felvstatusz_1
                                                               WHERE        (Deleted = 0) AND (Idfelvstatusz BETWEEN 6 AND 8)
                                                               GROUP BY Idjelentkezo))) AS B ON J.msk_kex_jelentkezokID = B.Idjelentkezo
WHERE        (J.Deleted = 0 OR j.Deleted=1) AND (LEN(J.ajanlo_nev) > 2) AND fs.Msk_kex_felvstatuszID IN
                             (SELECT        MAX(Msk_kex_felvstatuszID) AS ID
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz AS msk_kex_felvstatusz_1
                               WHERE        (Deleted = 0) AND (Idfelvstatusz BETWEEN 6 AND 8)
                               GROUP BY Idjelentkezo)
UNION
SELECT        J.msk_kex_jelentkezokID, J.datum, J.hp_nev, J.ajanlo_nev, A.targy, J.nev, F.LookupValue AS felveve, B.Ddatum AS ujfelveteldatum, A.idceg, A.reszleg, A.munkavegzes_helye, A.idvezeto, A.idtoborzo1, A.idtoborzo2, 
                         J.idallasajanlat, p2.Name AS toborzo_name2, p1.Name AS toborzo_name1, J.map_beerkezes, m.LookupValue AS map_dokumentacionev
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS J LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz AS fs ON fs.Idjelentkezo = J.msk_kex_jelentkezokID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_LookupList AS F ON F.LookupListID = fs.Idfelvstatusz LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_LookupList AS m ON J.idmap_dokumentacio = m.LookupListID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok AS A ON J.idallasajanlat = A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.People AS p1 ON A.idtoborzo1 = p1.PeopleID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.People AS p2 ON p2.PeopleID = A.idtoborzo2 LEFT JOIN
                             (SELECT        Idjelentkezo, CASE idfelvstatusz WHEN 6 THEN Belepesdatum ELSE NULL END AS Ddatum
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz
                               WHERE        (Msk_kex_felvstatuszID IN
                                                             (SELECT        Msk_kex_felvstatuszID AS ID
                                                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz AS msk_kex_felvstatusz_1
                                                               ))) AS B ON J.msk_kex_jelentkezokID = B.Idjelentkezo
WHERE        (J.Deleted = 0 OR j.Deleted=1) AND (LEN(J.ajanlo_nev) > 2) AND fs.Msk_kex_felvstatuszID IS NULL
GO
EXECUTE sp_addextendedproperty @name = N'MS_DiagramPaneCount', @value = 2, @level0type = N'SCHEMA', @level0name = N'dbo', @level1type = N'VIEW', @level1name = N'msk_kex_map_riport';




GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_rip_jelentkezok.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_rip_jelentkezok
AS
SELECT        a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID, a.targy, j.nev, j.email, j.telefonszam, j.berigeny, j.ajanlo_nev, j.datum, j.honnanertesult, 
                         ISNULL(toborzoID.LookupValue, 'Nincs �rt�kelve') AS toborzovelemenye, j.cv_toborzo_megj, ISNULL(vezetoID.LookupValue, 'Nincs �rt�kelve') AS vezetovelemenye, j.cv_vezeto_megj, 
                         ISNULL(felvetelID.LookupValue, 'Nincs kit�ltve') AS felvetelistatusz, a.idceg, a.idtoborzo1, p.Name AS toborzo1nev, a.munkavegzes_helye, ei.nev AS elutasitasnev, 
                         vi.nev AS visszalepesnev
FROM
dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok j
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok AS a ON a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=j.idallasajanlat
--LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_felvstatusz f ON f.Idjelentkezo=j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID AND f.Deleted = 0
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz f ON f.Idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_visszalepesindokok vi ON vi.msk_kex_visszalepesindokokID=f.Idvisszalepesindok
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_elutasitasindokok ei ON ei.msk_kex_elutasitasindokokID=f.Idelutasitasindok
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_LookupList felvetelID ON f.Idfelvstatusz = felvetelID.LookupListID
LEFT JOIN dbo.People p ON a.idtoborzo1 = p.PeopleID 
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_LookupList toborzoID ON j.idcv_toborzo = toborzoID.LookupListID 
LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_LookupList AS vezetoID ON j.idcv_vezeto = vezetoID.LookupListID

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_rip_jelentkezokforrasa.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_rip_jelentkezokforrasa
AS
SELECT        J.idszin AS jelentkezotipusa, J.honnanertesult, A.datum_aktivalas, A.idtoborzo1, A.idtoborzo2, A.idceg, A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID, COUNT(*) AS fo, A.targy
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS J LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok AS A ON J.idallasajanlat = A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID
WHERE        (J.Deleted = 0) AND (A.Deleted = 0)
GROUP BY J.idszin, J.honnanertesult, A.datum_aktivalas, A.idtoborzo1, A.idtoborzo2, A.idceg, A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID, A.targy
GO

GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_rip_kivalasztasi_fazisok_1.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_rip_kivalasztasi_fazisok
AS
SELECT        jel.[msk_kex_jelentkezokID], jel.[nev] AS jelentkezoNeve, allas.[targy] AS pozicio, p.Name AS toborzo1name, 'Interj�' AS fazis, inte.[datum] AS datum, look.[LookupValue] AS interjunMegjelent, 
                         look2.[LookupValue] AS interjuEredmenye, inte.[megjegyzes] AS interjuMegjegyzes, NULL AS tesztTipusa, NULL AS tesztetMegirta, NULL AS tesztEredmenye, NULL AS tesztMegjegyzes, NULL AS orvosiTipusa, NULL 
                         AS orvositMegkezdte, NULL AS orvosinMegfelelt, allas.[idceg] AS vallalatFilter, allas.[targy] AS allasajanlatFilter, allas.[idvezeto] AS statuszolovezetoFilter, allas.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] AS mjgyFilter, 
                         allas.[idtoborzo1] AS toborzo1Filter, allas.[idtoborzo2] AS toborzo2Filter, jel.datum AS jel_datum
FROM            [dbo].[msk_kex_jelentkezok] jel INNER JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_interju] inte ON inte.[idjelentkezo] = jel.[msk_kex_jelentkezokID] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_allasajanlatok] allas ON jel.[idallasajanlat] = allas.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_Lookuplist] look ON look.[LookupListID] = inte.[idmegjelent] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_Lookuplist] look2 ON look2.[LookupListID] = inte.[ideredmeny] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[People] p ON p.PeopleID = allas.idtoborzo1
WHERE        (inte.Deleted = 0)
UNION
SELECT        jel.[msk_kex_jelentkezokID], jel.[nev] AS jelentkezoNeve, allas.[targy] AS pozicio, p.Name AS toborzo1name, 'Teszt' AS fazis, teszt.[datum] AS datum, NULL AS interjunMegjelent, NULL AS interjuEredmenye, NULL 
                         AS interjuMegjegyzes, tesztt.[nev] AS tesztTipusa, look.[LookupValue] AS tesztMegirta, look2.[LookupValue] AS tesztEredmenye, teszt.[megjegyzes] AS tesztMegjegyzes, NULL AS orvosiTipusa, NULL AS orvositMegkezdte, NULL
                          AS orvosinMegfelelt, allas.[idceg] AS vallalatFilter, allas.[targy] AS allasajanlatFilter, allas.[idvezeto] AS statuszolovezetoFilter, allas.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] AS mjgyFilter, allas.[idtoborzo1] AS toborzo1Filter, 
                         allas.[idtoborzo2] AS toborzo2Filter, jel.datum AS jel_datum
FROM            [dbo].[msk_kex_jelentkezok] jel INNER JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_teszt] teszt ON teszt.[idjelentkezo] = jel.[msk_kex_jelentkezokID] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_teszttipusok] tesztt ON tesztt.[msk_kex_teszttipusokID] = teszt.[idteszttipus] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_allasajanlatok] allas ON jel.[idallasajanlat] = allas.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_Lookuplist] look ON look.[LookupListID] = teszt.[idmegirta] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_Lookuplist] look2 ON look2.[LookupListID] = teszt.[ideredmeny] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[People] p ON p.PeopleID = allas.idtoborzo1
WHERE        (teszt.Deleted = 0)
UNION
SELECT        jel.[msk_kex_jelentkezokID], jel.[nev] AS jelentkezoNeve, allas.[targy] AS pozicio, p.Name AS toborzo1name, 'Orvosi' AS fazis, orv.[datum] AS datum, NULL AS interjunMegjelent, NULL AS interjuEredmenye, NULL 
                         AS interjuMegjegyzes, NULL AS tesztTipusa, NULL AS tesztMegirta, NULL AS tesztEredmenye, NULL AS tesztMegjegyzes, orvt.[nev] AS orvosiTipusa, look.[LookupValue] AS orvositMegkezdte, 
                         look2.[LookupValue] AS orvosinMegfelelt, allas.[idceg] AS vallalatFilter, allas.[targy] AS allasajanlatFilter, allas.[idvezeto] AS statuszolovezetoFilter, allas.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] AS mjgyFilter, 
                         allas.[idtoborzo1] AS toborzo1Filter, allas.[idtoborzo2] AS toborzo2Filter, jel.datum AS jel_datum
FROM            [dbo].[msk_kex_jelentkezok] jel INNER JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_orvosi] orv ON orv.[idjelentkezo] = jel.[msk_kex_jelentkezokID] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_orvositipusok] orvt ON orvt.[msk_kex_orvositipusokID] = orv.[idorvositipus] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_allasajanlatok] allas ON jel.[idallasajanlat] = allas.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_Lookuplist] look ON look.[LookupListID] = orv.[idelkezdte] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[msk_kex_Lookuplist] look2 ON look2.[LookupListID] = orv.[ideredmeny] LEFT JOIN
                         [dbo].[People] p ON p.PeopleID = allas.idtoborzo1
WHERE        (orv.Deleted = 0)
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_rip_kpiszk.sql =====


CREATE VIEW [dbo].[msk_kex_rip_kpiszk]
AS
SELECT DISTINCT 
                         a.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID] AS msk_kex_allasajanlatokID, a.[engedely_iktatoszama] AS engedely_iktatoszama, a.[engedely_datuma] AS engedely_datuma, a.[targy] AS targy, a.[poziciok_szama] AS poziciok_szama, 
                         a.[reszleg] AS reszleg, a.[idtoborzo1] AS idtoborzo1, p.[Name] AS Name,
                             (SELECT        CASE WHEN Deleted = 1 THEN 'Lez�rt' WHEN CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) > CAST(datum_lejarat AS DATE) THEN 'Kiv�laszt�s' WHEN CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) <= CAST(datum_lejarat AS DATE) 
                                                         THEN 'Toborz�s' END
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok
                               WHERE        msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID) AS statusz, aj.[datum] AS ajanlattetel_datum,
                             (SELECT        CASE WHEN EXISTS
                                                             (SELECT        *
                                                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok aa INNER JOIN
                                                                                         dbo.msk_kex_lezarasindokok ll ON ll.Msk_kex_lezarasindokokID = aa.Idlezarasindok
                                                               WHERE        aa.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID AND (ll.Indokok LIKE '%em volt megfelel� jel�lt%' OR
                                                                                         ll.Indokok LIKE '%poz�ci� visszavon�sra ker�lt%')) THEN
                                                             (SELECT        aa.datum_lezaras
                                                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok aa INNER JOIN
                                                                                         dbo.msk_kex_lezarasindokok ll ON ll.Msk_kex_lezarasindokokID = aa.Idlezarasindok
                                                               WHERE        aa.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID AND (ll.Indokok LIKE '%em volt megfelel� jel�lt%' OR
                                                                                         ll.Indokok LIKE '%poz�ci� visszavon�sra ker�lt%')) ELSE NULL END
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok
                               WHERE        msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID) AS lezaras_datum, a.[idceg] AS idceg, [dbo].[msk_kex_get_MJGYNeve] (a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID) AS Idvezeto_neve, j.nev
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok a LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.People p ON p.PeopleID = a.idtoborzo1 LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok j ON j.idallasajanlat = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_ajanlat aj ON aj.idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID 
						 --LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok v ON a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = v.Idallasajanlat
WHERE        aj.datum IS NOT NULL --AND v.Deleted = 0 AND v.Mjgy = 10
UNION ALL
SELECT DISTINCT a.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID], a.[engedely_iktatoszama], a.[engedely_datuma], a.[targy], a.[poziciok_szama], a.[reszleg], a.[idtoborzo1] AS idtoborzo1, p.[Name],
                             (SELECT        CASE WHEN Deleted = 1 THEN 'Lez�rt' WHEN CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) > CAST(datum_lejarat AS DATE) THEN 'Kiv�laszt�s' WHEN CAST(GETDATE() AS DATE) <= CAST(datum_lejarat AS DATE) 
                                                         THEN 'Toborz�s' END
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok
                               WHERE        msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID) AS statusz, aj.[datum] AS ajanlattetel_datum,
                             (SELECT        CASE WHEN EXISTS
                                                             (SELECT        *
                                                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok aa INNER JOIN
                                                                                         dbo.msk_kex_lezarasindokok ll ON ll.Msk_kex_lezarasindokokID = aa.Idlezarasindok
                                                               WHERE        aa.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID AND (ll.Indokok LIKE '%em volt megfelel� jel�lt%' OR
                                                                                         ll.Indokok LIKE '%poz�ci� visszavon�sra ker�lt%')) THEN
                                                             (SELECT        aa.datum_lezaras
                                                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok aa INNER JOIN
                                                                                         dbo.msk_kex_lezarasindokok ll ON ll.Msk_kex_lezarasindokokID = aa.Idlezarasindok
                                                               WHERE        aa.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID AND (ll.Indokok LIKE '%em volt megfelel� jel�lt%' OR
                                                                                         ll.Indokok LIKE '%poz�ci� visszavon�sra ker�lt%')) ELSE NULL END
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok
                               WHERE        msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID) AS lezaras_datum, a.idceg, [dbo].[msk_kex_get_MJGYNeve] (a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID) AS Idvezeto_neve, j.nev
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok a LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.People p ON p.PeopleID = a.idtoborzo1 LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok j ON j.idallasajanlat = a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID LEFT JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_ajanlat aj ON aj.idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID
						 --LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok v ON a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID =v.Idallasajanlat
WHERE        aj.datum IS NULL AND a.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID NOT IN
                             (SELECT        aa.[msk_kex_allasajanlatokID]
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok aa LEFT JOIN
                                                         dbo.People p ON p.PeopleID = aa.idtoborzo1 LEFT JOIN
                                                         dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok j ON j.idallasajanlat = aa.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID LEFT JOIN
                                                         dbo.msk_kex_ajanlat aj ON aj.idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID
                               WHERE        aj.datum IS NOT NULL)
			--AND v.Deleted=0 AND v.Mjgy=10GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_rip_visszalepes.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_rip_visszalepes
AS
SELECT        'visszal�p�si' AS tipus, D.nev AS OK, A.datum_aktivalas, A.idtoborzo1, A.idtoborzo2, A.idceg, A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS J LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok AS A ON J.idallasajanlat = A.msk_kex_allasajanlatokID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_visszalepesindokok AS D ON J.idvisszalepesindok = D.msk_kex_visszalepesindokokID
WHERE        (J.Deleted = 0) AND (A.Deleted = 0) AND (J.idvisszalepesindok > 0)
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_stvezeto.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_stvezeto
AS
SELECT        P.PeopleID, P.Name, P.PERNR, P.STLTX, V.Idallasajanlat
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok AS V LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.People AS P ON V.Idvezeto = P.PeopleID
WHERE        (V.Deleted = 0) AND (P.Deleted = 0) AND (V.Mjgy = 9) AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true'
GO

GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_szum_ajanlat.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_szum_ajanlat
AS
SELECT        j.idallasajanlat, COUNT(*) AS afo, MAX(a.datum) AS adatum
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_ajanlat AS a LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS j ON a.idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID
WHERE        (a.Deleted = 0)
GROUP BY j.idallasajanlat

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_szum_ajanlatelfogadva.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_szum_ajanlatelfogadva
AS
SELECT        j.idallasajanlat, COUNT(*) AS afo
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_ajanlat AS a LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok AS j ON a.idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID
WHERE        (a.Deleted = 0) AND (a.idelfogadva = 4)
GROUP BY j.idallasajanlat

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_szum_cvmegfelelt.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_szum_elutasitva
AS
SELECT        dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok.idallasajanlat, COUNT(*) AS efo
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok INNER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz ON dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok.msk_kex_jelentkezokID = dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz.Idjelentkezo
WHERE        (dbo.msk_kex_AktualisFelveteliStatusz.Idfelvstatusz = 7)
GROUP BY dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok.idallasajanlat

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_szum_interjufo.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_kex_szum_interjufo
AS
SELECT        j.idallasajanlat, COUNT(*) AS ifo
FROM            dbo.msk_kex_interju AS i LEFT OUTER JOIN
                             (SELECT DISTINCT idallasajanlat, msk_kex_jelentkezokID
                               FROM            dbo.msk_kex_jelentkezok) AS j ON i.idjelentkezo = j.msk_kex_jelentkezokID
WHERE        (i.Deleted = 0)
GROUP BY j.idallasajanlat

GROUP BY j.idallasajanlat

CREATE VIEW dbo.[msk_kex_UtolsoFS]

FROM            dbo.msk_kex_felvstatusz
WHERE        (Deleted = 0)
GROUP BY Idjelentkezo

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_kex_view_ajanlat.sql =====

CREATE VIEW [dbo].[msk_kex_view_ajanlat]
WITH SCHEMABINDING
AS
SELECT [msk_kex_ajanlatID]
      ,[idjelentkezo]
      ,[datum]
      ,[idelfogadva]
      ,[idtovabbi_egyeztetes]
      ,CASE WHEN PozicioID IS NULL THEN [PozicioIDLast] ELSE [PozicioID] END AS [PozicioID]
  FROM [dbo].[msk_kex_ajanlat]
  WHERE deleted=0
GO
CREATE UNIQUE CLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_kex_fixajanlatID]
    ON [dbo].[msk_kex_view_ajanlat]([msk_kex_ajanlatID] ASC) WITH (STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = ON);


GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_kex_fixajanlatPozicioID]
    ON [dbo].[msk_kex_view_ajanlat]([PozicioID] ASC) WITH (FILLFACTOR = 80, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = ON);


/* teszt:
select * from dbo.msk_kex_view_ajanlat
*/

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\Max2.sql =====

create function Max2(@val1 int, @val2 int)
returns int
as
begin
  if @val1 > @val2
    return @val1
  return isnull(@val2,@val1)
end

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\mfn_tob_getRovidNev.sql =====

/*
Created by gabor Horvath 2024.01.29
*/



CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[mfn_tob_getRovidNev]
(
	@KeresesikerelemID int
)
RETURNS VARCHAR(50)
AS
BEGIN
	return (SELECT UPPER(RovidNev) FROM msk_Company c, orn_szi_Company oc , dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk
 WHERE kk.idceg=oc.AllasVallalatKod AND oc.Vallalatkod=c.bukrs AND kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=@KeresesikerelemID)

END
/*
TEST:
select [dbo].[mfn_tob_getRovidNev](469)
*/

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\msk_tob_fn_elem_readonly.sql =====

-- =============================================
-- Author:		<Najdanovszki Kriszti�n>
-- Create date: 2020.01.24
-- Description:	
-- =============================================
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[msk_tob_fn_elem_readonly] (@ElemNeve VARCHAR(200), @UserID INT, @KKID INT, @AHID INT, @Statusz INT)
RETURNS BIT
AS BEGIN
	DECLARE @Result BIT
	
	SET @Result = 'true'
	
	IF @ElemNeve = 'Toborzasi_folyamatgazda'
		BEGIN
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 'false'
			END
		END

	IF @ElemNeve = 'Toborzo'
		BEGIN
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOB')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 'false'
			END
		END

	IF @ElemNeve = 'Statusz'
		BEGIN
			IF @Statusz = 20 OR @Statusz = ''	/*Terv*/
			 BEGIN
				IF @UserID IN (SELECT Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					OR @UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
												LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
												LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
											WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
													AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
					BEGIN
						SET @Result = 'false'
					END
			 END

			IF @Statusz = 25	/*Elk�ld�tt*/ 
			 BEGIN
				IF --@UserID IN (SELECT Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					--OR 
					@UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
												LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
												LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
											WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_TOBENG')
													AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
					BEGIN
						SET @Result = 'false'
					END
			 END

			IF @Statusz = 21	/*Enged�lyezett*/ 
			 BEGIN
				IF --@UserID IN (SELECT Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					--OR 
					@UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
												LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
												LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
											WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
													AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
					BEGIN
						SET @Result = 'false'
					END
			 END

			IF @Statusz = 22	/*Publik�lt*/ 
			 BEGIN
				IF @UserID IN (SELECT Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					--OR @UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
					OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
												LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
												LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
											WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
													pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
													AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0)
					BEGIN
						SET @Result = 'false'
					END
			 END

			--IF @Statusz = 23	/*Lej�rt*/ 
			-- BEGIN
			--	IF @UserID IN (SELECT Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
			--		OR @UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
			--		OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
			--									LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
			--									LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
			--								WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
			--										pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
			--										pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
			--										pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
			--										AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0)
			--		BEGIN
			--			SET @Result = 'false'
			--		END
			-- END

			--IF @Statusz = 24	/*Lez�rt*/ 
			-- BEGIN
			--	IF @UserID IN (SELECT Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
			--		OR @UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = @KKID)
			--		OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
			--									LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
			--									LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
			--								WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
			--										pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
			--										pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
			--										pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
			--										AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0)
			--		BEGIN
			--			SET @Result = 'false'
			--		END
			-- END
		END

	IF @ElemNeve = 'ITadmin'
		BEGIN
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA') 
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 'false'
			END
		END

	IF @ElemNeve = 'HOPadmin'
		BEGIN
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA') 
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
			BEGIN
				SET @Result = 'false'
			END
		END

	RETURN @Result
END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\msk_tob_fn_menu_lathatosag.sql =====

-- =============================================
-- Author:		<Najdanovszki Kriszti�n>
-- Create date: <Create Date, ,>
-- Description:	<Description, ,>
-- =============================================
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[msk_tob_fn_menu_lathatosag] (@MMName VARCHAR(200), @UserID INT, @AllasID INT)
RETURNS BIT
AS BEGIN
	DECLARE @Result BIT
	
	SET @Result = 'false'
	
	IF @MMName = 'MMMSKKEXKarrierExcel'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOB' 
											--OR pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXVEZ'
											)
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
						--OR @UserID IN (SELECT idmunkaltato FROM msk_kex_allasajanlatok where Deleted = 0)
						OR @UserID IN (SELECT idvezeto FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok where Deleted = 0)
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'MMMSKTOB'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOB' 
											--OR pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXVEZ'
											)
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
						OR @UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem where Deleted = 0)
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'MMMSKTOBEng'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' 
											--OR pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF' 
											--OR pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOB' 
											--OR pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXVEZ'
											)
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
						OR @UserID IN (SELECT Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem where Deleted = 0)
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'ScreenMSKKEXKodszotar'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'ToborzasiFolyg'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'Toborzo' AND @AllasID <> 0
			IF @UserID IN (SELECT idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE Deleted=0 AND msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@AllasID)
			OR @UserID IN (SELECT idtoborzo2 FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE Deleted=0 AND msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@AllasID)
			OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'Toborzo' AND @AllasID = 0
			IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOB')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
				SET @Result = 'true'

	IF @MMName = 'Vezeto'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT idvezeto FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok where Deleted = 0 AND Idallasajanlat=@AllasID)
			OR @UserID IN (SELECT idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE Deleted=0 AND msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@AllasID)
			OR @UserID IN (SELECT idtoborzo2 FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE Deleted=0 AND msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@AllasID)
			OR @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_HOPA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
				SET @Result = 'true'


	IF @MMName = 'IT_admin'
		IF @UserID IN (SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
									WHERE	(pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_ITA' OR
											pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_UITA')
											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND dbo.msk_aktivPeopleID(p.PeopleID)='true')
				SET @Result = 'true'

	RETURN @Result
END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\msk_tob_getKeptarDocID.sql =====




-- =============================================
-- Author:		Najdanpvszki Kriszti�n
-- Create date: 2021-11-29
-- Description:	DocumentID alapj�n visszaadja a dokumentum el�r�si �tvonal�t.
-- =============================================
CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[msk_tob_getKeptarDocID]
(
	@keptarID INT
)
RETURNS INT
AS 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @res INT = (SELECT DocumentID FROM dbo.msk_tob_keptar WHERE Msk_tob_keptarID=@keptarID)
		
	RETURN @res
END;

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\msk_tob_getma.sql =====

-- =============================================
-- Author:		Horv�th G�bor
-- Create date: 2024.01.29.
-- Description:	tob-ban a GETDATE helyett haszn�land�
-- =============================================
CREATE function [dbo].[msk_tob_getma] (
)
RETURNS datetime
AS BEGIN
	declare @dt datetime = dbo.msk_tob_getSetup('GETMA')
	if @dt is null or @dt<'1910-01-01' return getdate()
	declare @ma datetime
	set @ma = @dt;declare @t datetime = CONVERT (time, GETDATE())  ;set @ma = @ma + @t	--TEST ONLY 
	return @ma;
END

/* .........................................
TEST 
Az al�bbi r�szlet be�ll�tja konkr�t d�tumra majd vissza az aktu�lisra a d�tumot.
Az id�pont r�szlet mindig a napi aktu�lis id�t mutatja csak a d�tum �ll �t

EXEC dbo.msk_tob_setma '2022-12-12 12:12'
SELECT dbo.msk_tob_getma()
EXEC dbo.msk_tob_setma null
SELECT dbo.msk_tob_getma()

*/

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\msk_tob_getSetup.sql =====

-- =============================================
-- Author:		Horv�th G�bor
-- Create date: 2024.01.29
-- Description:	TOB ApplicationSetup
-- =============================================
CREATE  function [dbo].[msk_tob_getSetup] (@Code VARCHAR(1000)
)
RETURNS VARCHAR(1000)
AS BEGIN
	DECLARE @res VARCHAR(1000) = (SELECT TOP 1 CodeValue FROM dbo.FSYS_ApplicationSetup WHERE Code=CONCAT('TOB_',@Code) AND Deleted=0)	
	RETURN @res
END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_AdHoc_email_kuldes.sql =====

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_AdHoc_email_kuldes] @AllashID INT, @ElsoAlkalom BIT, @SessionUserID INT
AS 
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON
	SET ANSI_WARNINGS OFF

	DECLARE @Cimzettek TABLE (Cimzett INT)

	DECLARE @Statusz INT
		SET @Statusz = (SELECT TOP 1 StatuszID FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@AllashID)

	DECLARE @KKID INT
		SET	@KKID = (SELECT TOP 1 Idkeresesikerelem FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID = @AllashID)
	DECLARE @KKName VARCHAR(200)
		SET	@KKName = (SELECT TOP 1 Cim FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=@KKID)
	DECLARE @Toborzo1 INT = (SELECT TOP 1 Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=@KKID)
	DECLARE @Toborzo1Neve VARCHAR(1000) = (SELECT TOP 1 Name FROM dbo.People WHERE PeopleID=@Toborzo1)

	DECLARE @Letrehozo_vallalat INT
		SET @Letrehozo_vallalat = (SELECT TOP 1 c.VallalatKod FROM dbo.orn_SZI_Company c LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk ON kk.Idceg=c.AllasVallalatKod WHERE kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=@KKID)
	DECLARE @Letrehozo_vallalatID INT
		SET @Letrehozo_vallalatID = (SELECT TOP 1 CompanyID FROM dbo.orn_SZI_Company WHERE VallalatKod=@Letrehozo_vallalat)
	DECLARE @Letrehozo_vallalatRovidNev VARCHAR(40)
		SET @Letrehozo_vallalatRovidNev = (SELECT TOP 1 RovidNev FROM dbo.msk_Company WHERE BUKRS=@Letrehozo_vallalat)
	DECLARE @TemplateID INT
	SET @TemplateID = (SELECT top 1 EmailTemplateSampleID FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE technical_name=CONCAT('tob_',@Letrehozo_vallalatRovidNev,'_eng_mod') AND Deleted=0  AND CompanyID=@Letrehozo_vallalatID)

	DECLARE @tmp_Targy  VARCHAR(150) 
		SET @tmp_Targy = (SELECT top 1 EmailSubject FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE EmailTemplateSampleID=@TemplateID)
		SET @tmp_Targy = REPLACE(@tmp_Targy, '%allashirdetes_neve%', ISNULL(@KKName, ''))
	DECLARE @tmp_Szoveg_eredeti  VARCHAR(MAX) 
		SET @tmp_Szoveg_eredeti = (SELECT top 1 EmailBody FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE EmailTemplateSampleID=@TemplateID)

	DECLARE @SentToJelentkezoTablaID INT = 0

	DECLARE @base_url VARCHAR(8000) = (SELECT TOP 1 CodeValue FROM dbo.FSYS_ApplicationSetup WHERE Code='BaseURL' AND Deleted=0)
	DECLARE @url VARCHAR(8000) = '%base%MMMSKTOBToborzas/ScreenMSKTOBKeresesiKerelem'
	SET @url = REPLACE(@url, '%base%', ISNULL(@base_url, ''))

	IF @Statusz = 21
		INSERT INTO @Cimzettek SELECT kk.Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=ah.Idkeresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@AllashID

	IF @Statusz = 22 --Toborz�, enged�lyez�, folyamatgazda
		BEGIN
		INSERT INTO @Cimzettek SELECT kk.Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=ah.Idkeresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@AllashID
		--INSERT INTO @Cimzettek SELECT kk.Idengedelyezo FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=ah.Idkeresesikerelem WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@AllashID
		--INSERT INTO @Cimzettek SELECT p.PeopleID FROM People p 
		--										LEFT JOIN PeopleGroupsPeople pgp ON p.PeopleID = pgp.PeopleID
		--										LEFT JOIN People pp ON pgp.GroupID = pp.PeopleID
		--									WHERE pp.TechnicalName = 'Group_KEXTOBF'
		--											AND pgp.Deleted = 0 AND pp.Deleted = 0 AND p.Deleted = 0 AND p.BUKRS=@Letrehozo_vallalat
		END
		SET @TemplateID = (SELECT top 1 EmailTemplateSampleID FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE technical_name=CONCAT('tob_',@Letrehozo_vallalatRovidNev,'_engedelyezett') AND Deleted=0  AND CompanyID=@Letrehozo_vallalatID)

	DECLARE @MailSendLogID INT
	DECLARE @MyCursor CURSOR
	DECLARE @CimzettID INT
	DECLARE @Cimzett_neve VARCHAR(200)
	DECLARE @Cimzett_email VARCHAR(200)
	DECLARE @tmp_Szoveg VARCHAR(MAX)
		BEGIN
			SET @MyCursor = CURSOR FOR
			select Cimzett from @Cimzettek

				OPEN @MyCursor 
				FETCH NEXT FROM @MyCursor 
				INTO @CimzettID

				WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
				BEGIN
						SET @Cimzett_neve = (SELECT top 1 Name FROM dbo.People WHERE PeopleID=@CimzettID)
						SET @Cimzett_email = (SELECT top 1 Email FROM dbo.People WHERE PeopleID=@CimzettID)
						DECLARE @Letrehozo_alairas VARCHAR(8000)
						SET @Letrehozo_alairas = (SELECT TOP 1 Alairas
												FROM dbo.msk_kex_emailalairas
												WHERE PeopleID=@Toborzo1 AND Deleted=0)
						
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = @tmp_Szoveg_eredeti
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%cimzett%', ISNULL(@Cimzett_neve, 'C�mzett'))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%allashirdetes_neve%', ISNULL(@KKName, ''))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%link%', ISNULL(@url, ''))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%kuldo%', ISNULL(@Toborzo1Neve, ''))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%kuldo_alairas%', ISNULL(@Letrehozo_alairas, ''))

						INSERT INTO dbo.msk_MailSend_Log
						(
							Modul,
							Recipients,
							CopyRecipients,
							BlindCopyRecipients,
							Subject,
							Body,
							BodyFormat,
							Importance,
							FileAttachments,
							MailItemID,
							Created,
							Success,
							Deleted,
							EmailTemplateID,
							CreatedBy,
							SentToJelentkezoID,
							SentToJelentkezoTablaID
						)
						VALUES
						(   'TOB',        -- Modul - varchar(50)
							@Cimzett_email,        -- Recipients - varchar(260)
							NULL,        -- CopyRecipients - varchar(8000)
							NULL,        -- BlindCopyRecipients - varchar(8000)
							@tmp_Targy,        -- Subject - varchar(200)
							@tmp_Szoveg,        -- Body - varchar(max)
							'HTML',        -- BodyFormat - varchar(20)
							'Normal',        -- Importance - varchar(100)
							'',        -- FileAttachments - varchar(8000)
							0,         -- MailItemID - int
							GETDATE(), -- Created - datetime
							0,      -- Success - bit
							0,         -- Deleted - tinyint
							@TemplateID,         -- EmailTemplateID - int
							@SessionUserID,         -- CreatedBy - int
							@CimzettID,         -- SentToJelentkezoID - int
							0          -- SentToJelentkezoTablaID - tinyint
							)

							SET @MailSendLogID = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

							EXEC [dbo].[msk_SendMail_dll] 	
									@Modul = 'TOB',
									@Recipients = @Cimzett_email,
									@CopyRecipients  = '',
									@BlindCopyRecipients = NULL,
									@Subject = @tmp_Targy,
									@Body = @tmp_Szoveg,
									@BodyFormat = 'HTML',
									@Importance = 'Normal',
									@FileAttachments = NULL,
									@EmailTemplateID = @TemplateID,
									@CreatedBy = @SessionUserID,
									@CimzettID = @CimzettID,
									@CimzettTablaID = @SentToJelentkezoTablaID,
									@MailSendLogID = @MailSendLogID

						--exec [dbo].[msk_SendMail]
						--		@Modul = 'TOB',
						--		@Recipients = @Cimzett_email,
						--		@CopyRecipients  = '',
						--		@BlindCopyRecipients = NULL,
						--		@Subject = @tmp_Targy,
						--		@Body = @tmp_Szoveg,
						--		@BodyFormat = 'HTML',
						--		@Importance = 'Normal',
						--		@FileAttachments = NULL,
						--		@EmailTemplateID = @TemplateID,
						--		@CreatedBy = 1,
						--		@CimzettID = @CimzettID,
						--		@CimzettTablaID = @SentToJelentkezoTablaID

					
				  FETCH NEXT FROM @MyCursor
				  INTO @CimzettID
				END; 

				CLOSE @MyCursor;
				DEALLOCATE @MyCursor;
			END;
	IF @Statusz = 22 AND @ElsoAlkalom = 1 --MJGY, vezet�
		BEGIN
			DECLARE @Cimzettek_vezetok TABLE (Cimzett INT, Statuszolo TINYINT, Mjgy INT)
			INSERT INTO @Cimzettek_vezetok (Cimzett,Statuszolo,Mjgy) SELECT kkv.Idvezeto, kkv.Statuszolovezeto, kkv.Mjgy FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok kkv 
												INNER JOIN dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah ON ah.Idkeresesikerelem=kkv.Idkeresesikerelem
											WHERE  ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@AllashID AND kkv.Deleted=0
			DECLARE @IsStatuszolo TINYINT
			DECLARE @IsMjgy INT
			SET @TemplateID = ((SELECT TOP 1 EmailTemplateSampleID FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE  technical_name=CONCAT('tob_',@Letrehozo_vallalatRovidNev,'_mjgy') AND Deleted=0 AND CompanyID=@Letrehozo_vallalatID))
			SET @tmp_Szoveg_eredeti = (SELECT top 1 EmailBody FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE EmailTemplateSampleID=@TemplateID)
			SET @tmp_Targy = (SELECT top 1 EmailSubject FROM dbo.orn_szi_EmailTemplateSample WHERE EmailTemplateSampleID=@TemplateID)



			SET @MyCursor = CURSOR FOR
			select Cimzett,Statuszolo,Mjgy from @Cimzettek_vezetok

				OPEN @MyCursor 
				FETCH NEXT FROM @MyCursor 
				INTO @CimzettID,@IsStatuszolo,@IsMjgy

				WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
				BEGIN
						SET @Cimzett_neve = (SELECT top 1 Name FROM dbo.People WHERE PeopleID=@CimzettID)
						SET @Cimzett_email = (SELECT top 1 Email FROM dbo.People WHERE PeopleID=@CimzettID)
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = @tmp_Szoveg_eredeti
						SET @tmp_Targy = REPLACE(@tmp_Targy, '%allashirdetes_neve%', ISNULL(@KKName, ''))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%cimzett%', ISNULL(@Cimzett_neve, 'C�mzett'))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%allashirdetes_neve%', ISNULL(@KKName, ''))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%link%', ISNULL(@url, ''))
						SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%kuldo%', ISNULL(@Toborzo1Neve, ''))
						IF @IsStatuszolo = 1 SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%statuszolo%', 'st�tuszol�')
							ELSE SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%statuszolo%', '')
						IF @IsMjgy = 10 SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%vezeto_tipus%', 'munk�ltat�i jogk�r gyakorl�')
						IF @IsMjgy = 9 SET @tmp_Szoveg = REPLACE(@tmp_Szoveg, '%vezeto_tipus%', 'vezet�')

						INSERT INTO dbo.msk_MailSend_Log
						(
							Modul,
							Recipients,
							CopyRecipients,
							BlindCopyRecipients,
							Subject,
							Body,
							BodyFormat,
							Importance,
							FileAttachments,
							MailItemID,
							Created,
							Success,
							Deleted,
							EmailTemplateID,
							CreatedBy,
							SentToJelentkezoID,
							SentToJelentkezoTablaID
						)
						VALUES
						(   'TOB',        -- Modul - varchar(50)
							@Cimzett_email,        -- Recipients - varchar(260)
							NULL,        -- CopyRecipients - varchar(8000)
							NULL,        -- BlindCopyRecipients - varchar(8000)
							@tmp_Targy,        -- Subject - varchar(200)
							@tmp_Szoveg,        -- Body - varchar(max)
							'HTML',        -- BodyFormat - varchar(20)
							'Normal',        -- Importance - varchar(100)
							'',        -- FileAttachments - varchar(8000)
							0,         -- MailItemID - int
							GETDATE(), -- Created - datetime
							0,      -- Success - bit
							0,         -- Deleted - tinyint
							@TemplateID,         -- EmailTemplateID - int
							@SessionUserID,         -- CreatedBy - int
							@CimzettID,         -- SentToJelentkezoID - int
							0          -- SentToJelentkezoTablaID - tinyint
							)

							SET @MailSendLogID = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

							EXEC [dbo].[msk_SendMail_dll] 	
									@Modul = 'TOB',
									@Recipients = @Cimzett_email,
									@CopyRecipients  = '',
									@BlindCopyRecipients = NULL,
									@Subject = @tmp_Targy,
									@Body = @tmp_Szoveg,
									@BodyFormat = 'HTML',
									@Importance = 'Normal',
									@FileAttachments = NULL,
									@EmailTemplateID = @TemplateID,
									@CreatedBy = @SessionUserID,
									@CimzettID = @CimzettID,
									@CimzettTablaID = @SentToJelentkezoTablaID,
									@MailSendLogID = @MailSendLogID

					
				  FETCH NEXT FROM @MyCursor
				  INTO @CimzettID,@IsStatuszolo,@IsMjgy
				END; 

				CLOSE @MyCursor;
				DEALLOCATE @MyCursor;
			END;


END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_allashirdetescopy.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_allashirdetescopy] @prsID integer	
AS 
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON
	


		  /*LOG*/
	DECLARE @UserID INT
	DECLARE @UserSession TABLE (
			[UserID] INT,
			[UserName] VARCHAR(250),
			[Language] VARCHAR(10)
	)
	INSERT INTO @UserSession EXECUTE [dbo].[osp_getPrsDataFromXml_UserSession] @prsID
	SELECT @UserID = (SELECT TOP 1 [UserID] FROM @UserSession)


	DECLARE @tmp_prs TABLE
	(
	ornAlias Varchar(100),
	ornType Varchar(100),
	ornValue Varchar(100),
	inOut Varchar(100)
	)
	INSERT INTO @tmp_prs execute osp_getPrsDataFromXml_Filters @prsID
	DECLARE @ID INT = (SELECT TOP 1 ornValue FROM @tmp_prs WHERE ornAlias='Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID_ID')


	insert into msk_tob_allashirdetesek ([Idkeresesikerelem]
      ,[Targy]
      ,[StatuszID]
      ,[Datum_lejarat]
      ,[CsatolmanyID]
      ,[Fejlecszoveg]
      ,[Feladatok]
      ,[Tulajdonsagok]
      ,[Elvarasok]
      ,[Elonytjelent]
      ,[Juttatasok]
      ,[Tovabbi_info]
      ,[Toborzo_info]
      ,[Toborzonev]
      ,[Toborzotelefonszam]
      ,[Vallalatibemutatkozo]
      ,[Datum_jovahagyas]
      ,[Datum_publikalas]
      ,[Link]
      ,[Datum_lezaras]
      ,[VegzettsegiszintID]
      ,[Pubcsoportportal]
      ,[PubCVO]
      ,[PubSTA]
      ,[Deleted]
      ,[FenykepURL]
	  ,[VideoURL]
      ,[LetrehozoID])
(select [Idkeresesikerelem]
      ,CONCAT([Targy],'_m�solat')
      ,20
      ,[Datum_lejarat]
      ,[CsatolmanyID]
      ,[Fejlecszoveg]
      ,[Feladatok]
      ,[Tulajdonsagok]
      ,[Elvarasok]
      ,[Elonytjelent]
      ,[Juttatasok]
      ,[Tovabbi_info]
      ,[Toborzo_info]
      ,[Toborzonev]
      ,[Toborzotelefonszam]
      ,[Vallalatibemutatkozo]
      ,[Datum_jovahagyas]
      ,[Datum_publikalas]
      ,[Link]
      ,[Datum_lezaras]
      ,[VegzettsegiszintID]
      ,0
      ,0
      ,0
      ,0
      ,[FenykepURL]
	  ,[VideoURL]
      ,@UserID
from msk_tob_allashirdetesek WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID = @ID)

/*
	declare @sel nvarchar(500)
	set @sel = 'Update Msk_tob_allashirdetesek set PubCVO=''@PubCVO'', PubSTA=''@PubSTA'', Pubcsoportportal=''@Pubcsoportportal'' WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID = @ID'

	exec sp_executesql @sel
	*/
	SELECT 'L�trej�tt az �j �ll�shirdet�s sz�veg!'

END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_allashirdeteslink.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_allashirdeteslink] @allasID INTEGER, @link VARCHAR(2000) 	
AS 
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON
	


	DECLARE @Success BIT

	UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek SET Link=@link ,statuszCSP=1, Datum_publikalas = GETDATE()
	WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@allasID
	
	/* LOG */
	INSERT INTO dbo.msk_log	(name,value,created) VALUES	('T�rolt be�rta a LINK-et amit az interf�szt�l kapott az �ll�shot:', @link, SYSDATETIME())
    
	/*V�lasz a DLL-nek*/
	SET @Success = 'true'
	SELECT @Success

END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_allashirdetespub.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_allashirdetespub] @allasID INTEGER, @PubCSP TINYINT, @PubCVO TINYINT, @PubSTA TINYINT
AS 
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON
	SET ANSI_WARNINGS OFF

	INSERT INTO dbo.msk_log
	(
	    name,
	    value,
	    created
	)
	VALUES
	(   'PubCSP-t�roltban',           -- name - varchar(100)
	    @PubCSP,           -- value - varchar(max)
	    SYSDATETIME() -- created - datetime2(7)
	    )

	/* Pip�k lement�se a formr�l �s st�tusz�t�ll�t�s*/
	UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek SET StatuszID=22, Pubcsoportportal=@PubCSP, PubCVO=@PubCVO, PubSTA=@PubSTA
	WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@allasID

	DECLARE @Success BIT

      DECLARE @id INT
      DECLARE @company VARCHAR(100)
      DECLARE @title VARCHAR(255)
      DECLARE @description VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @location VARCHAR(250)
      DECLARE @category INT
      DECLARE @companyid INT
      DECLARE @requirements VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @qualities VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @benefits VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @activationDate DATE
      DECLARE @expirationDate DATE
      DECLARE @contract VARCHAR(250)
      DECLARE @vacancyNumber INT
      DECLARE @workLocation VARCHAR(250)
      DECLARE @tasks VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @additionalInfo VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @recruiterInfo VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @recruiterId VARCHAR(10)
      DECLARE @recruiterEmail VARCHAR(100)
      DECLARE @industry VARCHAR(MAX)
      DECLARE @hierarchyLeve VARCHAR(200)
      DECLARE @educationType VARCHAR(250)
      DECLARE @educationField VARCHAR(250)
      DECLARE @Idtoborzo1 INT
      DECLARE @Idtoborzo2 INT
      DECLARE @Engedelyezesidatum DATE
      DECLARE @Iktatoszam VARCHAR(50)
	  DECLARE @FoglalkoztatasifokID INT
	  DECLARE @Link VARCHAR(2000)
	  DECLARE @MAPJob TINYINT
	  DECLARE @Cv TINYINT
	  DECLARE @VideoURL VARCHAR(1000)
	  DECLARE @properties VARCHAR(MAX)

	SELECT
	   @id=[id]
      ,@company=[company]
      ,@title=[title]
      ,@description=[description]
      ,@location=[location]
      ,@category=[category]
      ,@companyid=[companyid]
      ,@requirements=[requirements]
      ,@qualities=[qualities]
      ,@benefits=[benefits]
      ,@activationDate=[activationDate]
      ,@expirationDate=[expirationDate]
      ,@contract=[contract]
      ,@vacancyNumber=[vacancyNumber]
      ,@workLocation=[workLocation]
      ,@tasks=[tasks]
      ,@additionalInfo=[additionalInfo]
      ,@recruiterInfo=[recruiterInfo]
      ,@recruiterId=[recruiterId]
      ,@recruiterEmail=[recruiterEmail]
      ,@industry=[industry]
      ,@hierarchyLeve=[hierarchyLeve]
      ,@educationType=[educationType]
      ,@educationField=[educationField]
      ,@Idtoborzo1=[Idtoborzo1]
      ,@Idtoborzo2=[Idtoborzo2]
      ,@Engedelyezesidatum=[Engedelyezesidatum]
      ,@Iktatoszam=[Iktatoszam]
	  ,@FoglalkoztatasifokID=[schedule]
	  ,@Link=[Link]
	  ,@MAPJob=MAPJob
	  ,@Cv=Cv
	  ,@VideoURL=recruiterFelvado
	  ,@properties=properties
	  FROM [dbo].[msk_tob_portalallashirdetes]
	  WHERE id=@allasID

	  IF EXISTS(SELECT * FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@allasID)
		  BEGIN
			UPDATE dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok 
				SET 
					targy=@title,
					leiras=@description,
					hely=@location,
					idkategoria=@category,
					datum_aktivalas=@activationDate,
					datum_lejarat=@expirationDate,
					szerzodes_fajta=@contract,
					foglalkoztatasi_fok=@FoglalkoztatasifokID,
					poziciok_szama=@vacancyNumber,
					munkavegzes_helye=@workLocation,
					feladatok=@tasks,
					elvarasok=@requirements,
					elonytjelent=@qualities,
					juttatasok=@benefits,
					tovabbi_info=@additionalInfo,
					toborzo_info=@recruiterInfo,
					toborzo_torzsszam=@recruiterId,
					igazgatosag=@industry,
					munkakor_csoport=@hierarchyLeve,
					kepzes_fajta=@educationType,
					kepzes_szakirany=@educationField,
					toborzo_email=@recruiterEmail,
					toborzo_felvado=@VideoURL,
					map_job=@MAPJob,
					cv=@Cv,
					engedely_datuma=@Engedelyezesidatum,
					pozicio_szama=@vacancyNumber,
					idceg=@companyid,
					link=@Link,
					idtoborzo1=@Idtoborzo1,
					idtoborzo2=@Idtoborzo2,
					engedely_iktatoszama=@Iktatoszam,
					Tulajdonsagok=@properties
			WHERE msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@allasID 	
			
			INSERT INTO dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok
			(
				Idvezeto,
				Idallasajanlat,
				Mjgy,
				Deleted,
				Statuszolovezeto
			)
			(SELECT kkv.Idvezeto,
				@allasID,
				kkv.Mjgy,
				0,
				kkv.Statuszolovezeto	
				FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=ah.Idkeresesikerelem
													LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok kkv ON kkv.Idkeresesikerelem=kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID
				WHERE ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@allasID AND kkv.Deleted=0
				AND NOT EXISTS(SELECT * FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok WHERE Idallasajanlat=@allasID AND Idvezeto=kkv.Idvezeto AND Deleted=0))	

			/*E-mail k�ld�sek els� publik�l�skor*/
			EXEC dbo.msk_tob_AdHoc_email_kuldes @allasID, 0, 1
		  END
	  ELSE
		  BEGIN
			IF (SELECT TOP 1 toborzo_feluliras_flag FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@allasID)=1
				BEGIN
					SET @Idtoborzo1=(SELECT TOP 1 @Idtoborzo1 FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@allasID)
					SET @Idtoborzo2=(SELECT TOP 1 @Idtoborzo2 FROM dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok WHERE msk_kex_allasajanlatokID=@allasID)
                END
				
			INSERT INTO dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlatok
			(
			    msk_kex_allasajanlatokID,
			    uzletag,
			    targy,
			    leiras,
			    hely,
			    idkategoria,
			    idceg,
			    reszleg,
			    elvarasok,
			    elonytjelent,
			    juttatasok,
			    datum_aktivalas,
			    datum_lejarat,
			    szerzodes_fajta,
			    foglalkoztatasi_fok,
			    poziciok_szama,
			    munkavegzes_helye,
			    feladatok,
			    tovabbi_info,
			    toborzo_info,
			    toborzo_torzsszam,
			    vallalat,
			    igazgatosag,
			    munkakor_csoport,
			    kepzes_fajta,
			    kepzes_szakirany,
			    szak,
			    idegen_nyelv,
			    informatika,
			    szakmai_tapasztalat,
			    jogositvany,
			    link,
			    toborzo_feluliras_flag,
			    idszin,
			    idtoborzo1,
			    idtoborzo2,
			    idvezeto,
			    datum_tanfolyam,
			    idtanfolyamhely,
			    idtanfolyamtipus,
			    datum_lezaras,
			    aktiv,
			    datum_tanfolyam_szoveges,
			    min_tapasztalat,
			    min_vegzettseg,
			    vezetoi_engedely,
			    alt_ceg_nev,
			    alt_email,
			    alt_telefon,
			    ceg_elrejtese,
			    jelentkezes_gomb,
			    idfogado,
			    toborzo_email,
			    toborzo_felvado,
			    map_job,
			    cv,
			    kvalifikacio,
			    engedely_iktatoszama,
			    engedely_datuma,
			    pozicio_szama,
			    Deleted,
			    idmunkaltato,
			    Created,
			    Idlezarasindok,
				Tulajdonsagok
			)
			VALUES
			(   @allasID,         -- msk_kex_allasajanlatokID - int
			    @company,        -- uzletag - varchar(100)
			    @title,        -- targy - varchar(255)
			    @description,        -- leiras - varchar(max)
			    @location,        -- hely - varchar(255)
			    @category,         -- idkategoria - int
			    @companyid,         -- idceg - int
			    NULL,        -- reszleg - varchar(255)
			    @requirements,        -- elvarasok - varchar(max)
			    @qualities,        -- elonytjelent - varchar(max)
			    @benefits,        -- juttatasok - varchar(max)
			    @activationDate, -- datum_aktivalas - date
			    @expirationDate, -- datum_lejarat - date
			    @contract,        -- szerzodes_fajta - varchar(255)
			    @FoglalkoztatasifokID,        -- foglalkoztatasi_fok - varchar(50)
			    @vacancyNumber,         -- poziciok_szama - int
			    @workLocation,        -- munkavegzes_helye - varchar(255)
			    @tasks,        -- feladatok - varchar(max)
			    @additionalInfo,        -- tovabbi_info - varchar(max)
			    @recruiterInfo,        -- toborzo_info - varchar(max)
			    @recruiterId,        -- toborzo_torzsszam - varchar(10)
			    NULL,        -- vallalat - varchar(3)
			    @industry,        -- igazgatosag - varchar(4)
			    @hierarchyLeve,        -- munkakor_csoport - varchar(4)
			    @educationType,        -- kepzes_fajta - varchar(4)
			    @educationField,        -- kepzes_szakirany - varchar(4)
			    NULL,        -- szak - varchar(255)
			    NULL,        -- idegen_nyelv - varchar(max)
			    NULL,        -- informatika - varchar(max)
			    NULL,        -- szakmai_tapasztalat - varchar(max)
			    NULL,        -- jogositvany - varchar(max)
			    @Link,        -- link - varchar(2000)
			    0,         -- toborzo_feluliras_flag - tinyint
			    NULL,         -- idszin - int
			    @Idtoborzo1,         -- idtoborzo1 - int
			    @Idtoborzo2,         -- idtoborzo2 - int
			    0,         -- idvezeto - int
			    NULL, -- datum_tanfolyam - date
			    0,         -- idtanfolyamhely - int
			    0,         -- idtanfolyamtipus - int
			    NULL, -- datum_lezaras - date
			    0,         -- aktiv - tinyint
			    NULL,       -- datum_tanfolyam_szoveges - nchar(7)
			    0,         -- min_tapasztalat - int
			    0,         -- min_vegzettseg - int
			    NULL,      -- vezetoi_engedely - bit
			    NULL,        -- alt_ceg_nev - varchar(50)
			    NULL,        -- alt_email - varchar(50)
			    NULL,        -- alt_telefon - varchar(50)
			    NULL,      -- ceg_elrejtese - bit
			    NULL,      -- jelentkezes_gomb - bit
			    NULL,         -- idfogado - int
			    @recruiterEmail,        -- toborzo_email - varchar(255)
			    @VideoURL,        -- toborzo_felvado - varchar(255)
			    @MAPJob,         -- map_job - int
			    @Cv,         -- cv - int
			    NULL,        -- kvalifikacio - varchar(255)
			    @Iktatoszam,        -- engedely_iktatoszama - varchar(255)
			    @Engedelyezesidatum, -- engedely_datuma - date
			    @vacancyNumber,         -- pozicio_szama - int
			    0,         -- Deleted - tinyint
			    0,         -- idmunkaltato - int
			    GETDATE(), -- Created - datetime
			    NULL,          -- Idlezarasindok - int
				@properties    --Tulajdonsagok varchar(MAX)
 			    )

			INSERT INTO dbo.msk_kex_allasajanlat_vezetok
			(
				Idvezeto,
				Idallasajanlat,
				Mjgy,
				Deleted,
				Statuszolovezeto
			)
			(SELECT kkv.Idvezeto,
				@allasID,
				kkv.Mjgy,
				0,
				kkv.Statuszolovezeto	
				FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem kk ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=ah.Idkeresesikerelem
													LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok kkv ON kkv.Idkeresesikerelem=kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID
				WHERE ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@allasID AND kkv.Deleted=0)

			/*E-mail k�ld�sek els� publik�l�skor*/
			EXEC dbo.msk_tob_AdHoc_email_kuldes @allasID, 1, 1
		  END

    
	/* LOG */
	INSERT INTO dbo.msk_log	(name,value,created) VALUES	('T�rolt bem�solta a KEX-be az �ll�saj�nlatot', @allasID, SYSDATETIME())

	/* friss�ti az msk_kex_advertlistchangelog t�bl�t */
    EXEC [dbo].[msk_tob_msk_kex_advertlistchangelog_frissites] @allasID

	/*V�lasz a DLL-nek*/
	SET @Success = 'true'
	SELECT @Success

END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_CVO_DLL_select.sql =====

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_CVO_DLL_select] 
AS
BEGIN
select (
select PID as "@ID",
ISNULL(case when ltrim(PCOMPANY)='' then '-' else PCOMPANY END,'') as company,
ISNULL(PTITLE,'') as title, 
ISNULL(PDESCRIPTION,'') as description, 
ISNULL(plocation,'') as 'locations/location', 
ISNULL(pcategory,'') as 'categories/category',
ISNULL(PcompanyID,'') as companyID, 
ISNULL(pdepartment,'') as department, 
ISNULL(prequirements,'') as requirements, 
ISNULL(pqualities,'') as qualities, 
ISNULL(pbenefits,'') as benefits, 
ISNULL(pminexperience,'') as min_experience, 
ISNULL(pmineducation,'') as min_education, 
ISNULL(pdriverlicence,'') as driver_license,
ISNULL(plink,'') as link, 
ISNULL(pactivationdate,'') as activation_date, 
ISNULL(pexpirationdate,'') as expiration_date, 
ISNULL(pcontract,'') as contract, 
ISNULL(pschedule,'') as schedule, 
ISNULL(pcompanyname,'') as company_name, 
ISNULL(pemail,'') as email, 
ISNULL(pphone,'') as phone, 
ISNULL(PVACANCYNUMBER,'') as vacancy_nr, 
ISNULL(pworklocation,'') as work_location, 
'false' as hide_company, 
'false' as show_apply_button, 
ISNULL(pcustomtemplateID,'') as custom_template_ID, 
ISNULL(ptasks,'') as tasks, 
ISNULL(padditionalinfo,'') as additional_info, 
ISNULL(precruiterinfo,'') as recruiter_info, 
ISNULL(pfenykepurl,'') as fenykepurl,
ISNULL(pvideourl,'') as videourl,
ISNULL(pproperties,'') as properties
from msk_tob_CVO /* where padditionalinfo is not null and padditionalinfo<>'' */
for xml path('advert'), root('WebAdverts')
) as xml
end

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_CVO_item] 
@ID int
AS
BEGIN
	update msk_tob_allashirdetesek set StatuszCVO=1 where Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID = @ID


	insert into msk_log (name,value,created) values ('CVO Interf�sz ITEM OK',@ID,getdate())
	select 'True'
END
