===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_keresesikerelem_masolas.sql =====

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_masolas] @ID integer	
AS 
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON
	
	DECLARE @tmp_prs TABLE
	(
		ornAlias Varchar(100),
		ornType Varchar(100),
		ornValue Varchar(100),
		inOut Varchar(100)
	)
	INSERT INTO @tmp_prs execute osp_getPrsDataFromXml_Filters @ID
	DECLARE @idkkmasolas INT = (SELECT TOP 1 ornValue FROM @tmp_prs WHERE ornAlias='Template_MSKTOBKeresesiKerelemMasolas')
	DECLARE @kkID INT = (SELECT TOP 1 ornValue FROM @tmp_prs WHERE ornAlias='Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID_ID')

	DECLARE @tmp_user TABLE(
	UserID INT,UserName VARCHAR(100),Language VARCHAR(100))
	INSERT INTO @tmp_user EXECUTE dbo.osp_getPrsDataFromXml_UserSession @ID
	DECLARE @UserID INT = (SELECT TOP 1 UserID FROM @tmp_user)

	DECLARE @UjKK INT


  IF @idkkmasolas = 1 OR @idkkmasolas = 2
	BEGIN

		  INSERT INTO dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem
		  (
		      Cim,
		      StatuszID,
		      Iktatoszam,
		      Engedelyezesidatum,
		      Munkakor,
		      Lejaratidatum,
		      Pozicioszam,
		      TeruletiigazgatosagID,
		      SzakteruletID,
		      SzervezetiegyesegID,
		      SzerzodesfajtaID,
		      MunkavegzeshelyeID,
		      Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb,
		      Cv,
		      MunkakorcsoportID,
		      FoglalkoztatasifokID,
		      Kepzes_fajtaID,
		      Kepzes_szakiranyID,
		      MMKkod,
		      Berlatszik,
		      Berkotelezo,
		      Map_job,
		      Idtoborzo1,
		      Idtoborzo2,
		      Idengedelyezo,
		      Idceg,
		      Deleted,
		      Szerzodes_befejezes,
		      Lezaras
		  )
		  (SELECT
			   CONCAT([Cim],'_m�solat')
			  ,NULL
			  ,[Iktatoszam]
			  ,[Engedelyezesidatum]
			  ,[Munkakor]
			  ,NULL
			  ,[Pozicioszam]
			  ,[TeruletiigazgatosagID]
			  ,[SzakteruletID]
			  ,[SzervezetiegyesegID]
			  ,[SzerzodesfajtaID]
			  ,[MunkavegzeshelyeID]
			  ,[Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb]
			  ,[Cv]
			  ,[MunkakorcsoportID]
			  ,[FoglalkoztatasifokID]
			  ,[Kepzes_fajtaID]
			  ,[Kepzes_szakiranyID]
			  ,[MMKkod]
			  ,[Berlatszik]
			  ,[Berkotelezo]
			  ,[Map_job]
			  ,[Idtoborzo1]
			  ,[Idtoborzo2]
			  ,[Idengedelyezo]
			  ,[Idceg]
			  ,0
			  ,[Szerzodes_befejezes]
			  ,0
			FROM [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]
			WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=@kkID)

		SET @UjKK = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

	END

	IF @idkkmasolas = 1
	BEGIN
		BEGIN TRAN
		DECLARE @msk_tob_allashirdetesek TABLE
			(
			[Idkeresesikerelem] [INT] NULL,
			[Targy] [VARCHAR](255) NULL,
			[StatuszID] [INT] NULL,
			[Datum_lejarat] [DATE] NULL,
			[CsatolmanyID] [INT] NULL,
			[Fejlecszoveg] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Feladatok] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Tulajdonsagok] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Elvarasok] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Elonytjelent] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Juttatasok] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Tovabbi_info] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Toborzo_info] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Toborzonev] [VARCHAR](250) NULL,
			[Toborzotelefonszam] [VARCHAR](50) NULL,
			[Vallalatibemutatkozo] [VARCHAR](MAX) NULL,
			[Datum_jovahagyas] [DATE] NULL,
			[Datum_publikalas] [DATE] NULL,
			[Link] [VARCHAR](2000) NULL,
			[Datum_lezaras] [DATE] NULL,
			[VegzettsegiszintID] [INT] NULL,
			[Pubcsoportportal] [BIT] NULL,
			[PubCVO] [BIT] NULL,
			[PubSTA] [BIT] NULL,
			[FenykepURL] [VARCHAR](1000) NULL,
			[VideoURL] [VARCHAR](1000) NULL,
			[Deleted] [TINYINT] NULL,
			[LetrehozoID] [INT] NULL)

			INSERT INTO @msk_tob_allashirdetesek
			(
				Idkeresesikerelem,
				Targy,
				StatuszID,
				Datum_lejarat,
				CsatolmanyID,
				Fejlecszoveg,
				Feladatok,
				Tulajdonsagok,
				Elvarasok,
				Elonytjelent,
				Juttatasok,
				Tovabbi_info,
				Toborzo_info,
				Toborzonev,
				Toborzotelefonszam,
				Vallalatibemutatkozo,
				Datum_jovahagyas,
				Datum_publikalas,
				Link,
				Datum_lezaras,
				VegzettsegiszintID,
				Pubcsoportportal,
				PubCVO,
				PubSTA,
				Deleted,		
				LetrehozoID,
				FenykepURL,
				VideoURL
			)
			SELECT TOP 1
			   @UjKK AS Idkeresesikerelem
			  ,CONCAT([Targy],'_m�solat') AS Targy
			  ,20 AS StatuszID
			  ,NULL AS Datum_lejarat
			  ,[CsatolmanyID]
			  ,[Fejlecszoveg]
			  ,[Feladatok]
			  ,[Tulajdonsagok]
			  ,[Elvarasok]
			  ,[Elonytjelent]
			  ,[Juttatasok]
			  ,[Tovabbi_info]
			  ,[Toborzo_info]
			  ,[Toborzonev]
			  ,[Toborzotelefonszam]
			  ,[Vallalatibemutatkozo]
			  ,NULL AS Datum_jovahagyas
			  ,NULL AS Datum_publikalas
			  ,[Link]
			  ,NULL AS Datum_lezaras
			  ,[VegzettsegiszintID]
			  ,[Pubcsoportportal]
			  ,[PubCVO]
			  ,[PubSTA]
			  ,0 AS Deleted
			  ,@UserID AS LetrehozoID
			  ,FenykepURL
			  ,VideoURL
		  FROM [dbo].[msk_tob_allashirdetesek]
		  WHERE Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID AND Deleted=0
		  ORDER BY Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID DESC

		  INSERT INTO dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek
			(
				Idkeresesikerelem,Targy,StatuszID,Datum_lejarat,CsatolmanyID,Fejlecszoveg,Feladatok,
				Tulajdonsagok,Elvarasok,Elonytjelent,Juttatasok,Tovabbi_info,Toborzo_info,Toborzonev,
				Toborzotelefonszam,Vallalatibemutatkozo,Datum_jovahagyas,Datum_publikalas,Link,Datum_lezaras,
				VegzettsegiszintID,Pubcsoportportal,PubCVO,PubSTA,Deleted,LetrehozoID,FenykepURL,VideoURL)
			(SELECT Idkeresesikerelem,
					Targy,
					StatuszID,
					Datum_lejarat,
					CsatolmanyID,
					Fejlecszoveg,
					Feladatok,
					Tulajdonsagok,
					Elvarasok,
					Elonytjelent,
					Juttatasok,
					Tovabbi_info,
					Toborzo_info,
					Toborzonev,
					Toborzotelefonszam,
					Vallalatibemutatkozo,
					Datum_jovahagyas,
					Datum_publikalas,
					Link,
					Datum_lezaras,
					VegzettsegiszintID,
					Pubcsoportportal,
					PubCVO,
					PubSTA,
					Deleted,
					LetrehozoID,
					FenykepURL,
					VideoURL
			  FROM @msk_tob_allashirdetesek)
		COMMIT
	END
	
END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_keresesikerelem_masolas_betoltetlen.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_masolas_betoltetlen] 
	@kkID integer	--keresesikerelemID,
	,@UserID INT
AS 
BEGIN
	DECLARE @UjKK INT
	declare @UJSORSZAM bit = 0 -- 1 eset�n �j sorsz�mot gener�l a m�solt adatoknak #86289 

	declare @has int = (select count(*) from msk_tob_pozicio where deleted=0 and StatuszID=32 and Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID )

	if @has = 0 begin
		return
	end

		  INSERT INTO dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem
		  (
		      Cim,
		      StatuszID,
		      Iktatoszam,
		      Engedelyezesidatum,
		      Munkakor,
		      Lejaratidatum,
		      Pozicioszam,
		      TeruletiigazgatosagID,
		      SzakteruletID,
		      SzervezetiegyesegID,
		      SzerzodesfajtaID,
		      MunkavegzeshelyeID,
		      Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb,
		      Cv,
		      MunkakorcsoportID,
		      FoglalkoztatasifokID,
		      Kepzes_fajtaID,
		      Kepzes_szakiranyID,
		      MMKkod,
		      Berlatszik,
		      Berkotelezo,
		      Map_job,
		      Idtoborzo1,
		      Idtoborzo2,
		      Idengedelyezo,
		      Idceg,
		      Deleted,
		      Szerzodes_befejezes,
		      Lezaras
		  )
		  (SELECT
			   CONCAT([Cim],'_m�solat')
			  ,NULL
			  ,[Iktatoszam]
			  ,[Engedelyezesidatum]
			  ,[Munkakor]
			  ,NULL
			  ,[Pozicioszam]
			  ,[TeruletiigazgatosagID]
			  ,[SzakteruletID]
			  ,[SzervezetiegyesegID]
			  ,[SzerzodesfajtaID]
			  ,[MunkavegzeshelyeID]
			  ,[Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb]
			  ,[Cv]
			  ,[MunkakorcsoportID]
			  ,[FoglalkoztatasifokID]
			  ,[Kepzes_fajtaID]
			  ,[Kepzes_szakiranyID]
			  ,[MMKkod]
			  ,[Berlatszik]
			  ,[Berkotelezo]
			  ,[Map_job]
			  ,[Idtoborzo1]
			  ,[Idtoborzo2]
			  ,[Idengedelyezo]
			  ,[Idceg]
			  ,0
			  ,[Szerzodes_befejezes]
			  ,0
			FROM [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]
			WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID=@kkID)

		SET @UjKK = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

		INSERT INTO dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek
		(
		    Idkeresesikerelem,
		    Targy,
		    StatuszID,
		    Datum_lejarat,
		    CsatolmanyID,
		    Fejlecszoveg,
		    Feladatok,
		    Tulajdonsagok,
		    Elvarasok,
		    Elonytjelent,
		    Juttatasok,
		    Tovabbi_info,
		    Toborzo_info,
		    Toborzonev,
		    Toborzotelefonszam,
		    Vallalatibemutatkozo,
		    Datum_jovahagyas,
		    Datum_publikalas,
		    Link,
		    Datum_lezaras,
		    VegzettsegiszintID,
		    Pubcsoportportal,
		    PubCVO,
		    PubSTA,
		    Deleted,
		    LetrehozoID,
			FenykepURL,
			VideoURL
		)
		(SELECT 
			   @UjKK
			  ,CONCAT([Targy],'_m�solat')
			  ,20
			  ,NULL
			  ,[CsatolmanyID]
			  ,[Fejlecszoveg]
			  ,[Feladatok]
			  ,[Tulajdonsagok]
			  ,[Elvarasok]
			  ,[Elonytjelent]
			  ,[Juttatasok]
			  ,[Tovabbi_info]
			  ,[Toborzo_info]
			  ,[Toborzonev]
			  ,[Toborzotelefonszam]
			  ,[Vallalatibemutatkozo]
			  ,NULL
			  ,NULL
			  ,[Link]
			  ,NULL
			  ,[VegzettsegiszintID]
			  ,[Pubcsoportportal]
			  ,[PubCVO]
			  ,[PubSTA]
			  ,0
			  ,@UserID
			  ,FenykepURL
			  ,VideoURL
		  FROM [dbo].[msk_tob_allashirdetesek]
		  WHERE Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID AND Deleted=0)
	

	declare
     @VallalatRovidNeve VARCHAR(50) = (select [dbo].[mfn_tob_getRovidNev](@UjKK))
	,@tanfolyamos BIT = (select top 1 case when Poziciotipus=41 then 1 else 0 end from msk_tob_headpozicio where deleted=0 and Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID ) 
    ,@mennyiseg INT = @has
	,@datum date = (select top 1 engedelyezesidatum from msk_tob_pozicio where deleted=0 and StatuszID=32 and Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID order by PozicioID)
	,@PozicioInfo varchar(50)
	,@ikt varchar(max)
	,@Alszam int =0
	,@Stat2 int
	,@ID int = 0		
	,@IDCursor CURSOR

	if @UJSORSZAM=1 begin
		if @tanfolyamos = 1 begin
			EXEC msp_tob_getIktatoszam @UjKK,@VallalatRovidNeve,@tanfolyamos,@mennyiseg,@datum,''
		end
		else begin
			SET @IDCursor = CURSOR FOR select PozicioID from msk_tob_pozicio where deleted=0 and StatuszID=32 and Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID order by pozicioID
			OPEN @IDCursor
			FETCH NEXT FROM @IDCursor INTO @ID
			WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
			BEGIN
				select top 1 @datum=engedelyezesidatum,@PozicioInfo=PozicioInfo from msk_tob_pozicio where PozicioID=@ID
				EXEC msp_tob_getIktatoszam @UjKK,@VallalatRovidNeve,@tanfolyamos,1,@datum,@PozicioInfo
				FETCH NEXT FROM @IDCursor INTO @ID
			END;
			CLOSE @IDCursor;
			DEALLOCATE @IDCursor;
	
		end
	end else begin
			set @ID = 0		
			SET @IDCursor = CURSOR FOR select PozicioID from msk_tob_pozicio where deleted=0 and StatuszID=32 and Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID order by pozicioID
			OPEN @IDCursor
			FETCH NEXT FROM @IDCursor INTO @ID
			WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
			BEGIN
				select top 1 @Stat2=StatuszID,@ikt=Iktatoszam,@datum=engedelyezesidatum,@PozicioInfo=PozicioInfo from msk_tob_pozicio where PozicioID=@ID
				SET @Alszam = CONVERT(INT, RIGHT(@ikt, 3)) ;

				INSERT INTO msk_tob_pozicio (Idkeresesikerelem, Iktatoszam, Aliktatoszam, Engedelyezesidatum, StatuszID, Deleted,PozicioInfo)
				VALUES (@UjKK, @ikt, @Alszam, @datum, @Stat2,0,@PozicioInfo);

				FETCH NEXT FROM @IDCursor INTO @ID
			END;
			CLOSE @IDCursor;
			DEALLOCATE @IDCursor;

			INSERT INTO msk_tob_headpozicio (Idkeresesikerelem, Poziciotipus, Iktatoszam, Engedelyezesidatum, Deleted,Automata,AutomataKKID)
			select top 1 @UjKK,Poziciotipus, Iktatoszam, Engedelyezesidatum, 0,dbo.msk_tob_getma(),@kkID  from msk_tob_headpozicio where Idkeresesikerelem=@kkID			
	end

END

/*

*/


===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_msk_kex_advertlistchangelog_frissites.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_msk_kex_advertlistchangelog_frissites] @AllasID INT	
AS 
BEGIN

		--DECLARE @Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID INT
		--DECLARE @AdvertListID INT
		--DECLARE @WebAdvertsID INT
		DECLARE @AdvertID varchar(8000) = @AllasID
		DECLARE @Company varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @Title varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @Description varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @Locations varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @Categories varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @CompanyID varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @Department VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Requirements VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Qualities VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Benefits VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Min_Experience VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Min_Education VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Driver_Licence VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Link varchar(8000)
		DECLARE @Activation_Date VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Expiraton_Date VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Contract VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Schedule VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Company_Name VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Email VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Phone VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Vacancy_NR VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Work_Location VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Hide_Company VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Schow_Apply_Button VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Custom_Template_ID VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Tasks VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Additional_Info VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Recruiter_Info VARCHAR(8000)
		DECLARE @Recruiter_ID VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Recruiter_email VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Recruiter_Felvado VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Map_Job VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @CV VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Subsidiary VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Industry VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Hierarchy_Level VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Education_Type VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Education_Field VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Field_Of_Study VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Reference_Number VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Approval_Date VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Number_Of_Positions VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Created DATETIME 
		DECLARE @Deleted TINYINT

		--DECLARE @Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID_log INT 
		--DECLARE @AdvertListID_log INT 
		--DECLARE @WebAdvertsID_log INT 
		DECLARE @AdvertID_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @Company_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @Title_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @Description_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @Locations_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @Categories_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @CompanyID_log varchar(8000) 
		DECLARE @Department_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Requirements_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Qualities_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Benefits_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Min_Experience_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Min_Education_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Driver_Licence_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Link_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Activation_Date_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Expiraton_Date_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Contract_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Schedule_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Company_Name_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Email_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Phone_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Vacancy_NR_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Work_Location_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Hide_Company_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Schow_Apply_Button_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Custom_Template_ID_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Tasks_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Additional_Info_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Recruiter_Info_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Recruiter_id_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Recruiter_Email_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Recruiter_Felvado_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Map_Job_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @CV_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Subsidiary_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Industry_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Hierarchy_Level_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Education_Type_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Education_Field_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Field_Of_Study_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Reference_Number_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Approval_Date_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Number_Of_Positions_log VARCHAR(8000) 
		DECLARE @Created_log DATETIME 
		DECLARE @Deleted_log TINYINT 

		--Aktu�lis Keres�si k�relem �s �ll�shirdet�s lek�rdez�se
		SELECT 
		-- @Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID
		--,@AdvertListID
		--,@WebAdvertsID
		 @AdvertID = ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID
		,@Company = c.Name
		,@Title = ah.Targy
		,@Description = ah.Vallalatibemutatkozo
		,@Locations = CONCAT('<LOCATION>', t.Telepules, '</LOCATION>')
		,@Categories = k.SzakteruletID
		,@CompanyID = k.Idceg
		,@Department = k.SzakteruletID
		,@Requirements = ah.Elvarasok
		,@Qualities = ah.Elonytjelent
		,@Benefits = ah.Juttatasok
		,@Min_Experience = NULL
		,@Min_Education = NULL
		,@Driver_Licence = 'False'
		,@Link = ah.Link
		,@Activation_Date = ah.Datum_publikalas
		,@Expiraton_Date = ah.Datum_lejarat
		,@Contract = szf.Szerzodesfajta
		,@Schedule = k.FoglalkoztatasifokID
		,@Company_Name = NULL
		,@Email = NULL
		,@Phone = NULL
		,@Vacancy_NR = k.Pozicioszam
		,@Work_Location = t.Telepules
		,@Hide_Company = 'False'
		,@Schow_Apply_Button = 'False'
		,@Custom_Template_ID = NULL
		,@Tasks = ah.Feladatok
		,@Additional_Info = ah.Fejlecszoveg
		,@Recruiter_Info = ah.Toborzotelefonszam
		,@Recruiter_ID = p.PERNR
		,@Recruiter_email = p.Email 
		,@Recruiter_Felvado = ah.VideoURL
		,@Map_Job = k.Map_job 
		,@CV = k.Cv 
		,@Subsidiary = NULL
		,@Industry = k.TeruletiigazgatosagID
		,@Hierarchy_Level = k.MunkakorcsoportID
		,@Education_Type = k.Kepzes_fajtaID
		,@Education_Field = k.Kepzes_szakiranyID
		,@Field_Of_Study = ah.FenykepURL
		,@Reference_Number = k.Iktatoszam
		,@Approval_Date = k.Engedelyezesidatum
		,@Number_Of_Positions = k.Pozicioszam

		FROM dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem k 
		LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek ah ON ah.Idkeresesikerelem=k.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek t ON t.Msk_tob_telepulesekID=k.MunkavegzeshelyeID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.orn_SZI_Company c ON c.AllasVallalatKod=k.Idceg
		LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta szf ON szf.Msk_tob_szerzodesfajtaID = k.SzerzodesfajtaID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok ff ON ff.Msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifokID=k.FoglalkoztatasifokID
		LEFT JOIN dbo.People AS p ON k.Idtoborzo1 = p.PeopleID
		WHERE ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID=@AllasID
		
		--Legutols� advertlog id kinyer�se 
		DECLARE @MaxAdvertlistchangelogID INT
		SET @MaxAdvertlistchangelogID = (SELECT MAX(Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID) FROM dbo.msk_kex_advertlistchangelog WHERE AdvertID=@AdvertID)
		
		--Legutols� advertlog lek�rdez�se
		SELECT
		--,@Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID_log INT 
		--,@AdvertListID_log INT 
		--,@WebAdvertsID_log INT 
		 @AdvertID_log = AdvertID
		,@Company_log = Company
		,@Title_log = Title
		,@Description_log = Description
		,@Locations_log = Locations
		,@Categories_log = Categories
		,@CompanyID_log = CompanyID
		,@Department_log = Department
		,@Requirements_log = Requirements
		,@Qualities_log = Qualities
		,@Benefits_log = Benefits
		,@Min_Experience_log = Min_Experience
		,@Min_Education_log = Min_Education
		,@Driver_Licence_log = Driver_Licence
		,@Link_log = Link
		,@Activation_Date_log = Activation_Date
		,@Expiraton_Date_log = Expiraton_Date
		,@Contract_log = Contract
		,@Schedule_log = Schedule
		,@Company_Name_log = Company_Name
		,@Email_log = Email
		,@Phone_log = Phone
		,@Vacancy_NR_log = Vacancy_NR
		,@Work_Location_log = Work_Location
		,@Hide_Company_log = Hide_Company
		,@Schow_Apply_Button_log = Schow_Apply_Button
		,@Custom_Template_ID_log = Custom_Template_ID
		,@Tasks_log = Tasks
		,@Additional_Info_log = Additional_Info
		,@Recruiter_Info_log = Recruiter_Info
		,@Recruiter_id_log = Recruiter_ID
		,@Recruiter_Email_log = Recruiter_Email
		,@Recruiter_Felvado_log = Recruiter_Felvado
		,@Map_Job_log = Map_Job
		,@CV_log = CV
		,@Subsidiary_log = Subsidiary
		,@Industry_log = Industry
		,@Hierarchy_Level_log = Hierarchy_Level
		,@Education_Type_log = Education_Type
		,@Education_Field_log = Education_Field
		,@Field_Of_Study_log = Field_Of_Study
		,@Reference_Number_log = Reference_Number
		,@Approval_Date_log = Approval_Date
		,@Number_Of_Positions_log = Number_Of_Positions
		FROM dbo.msk_kex_advertlistchangelog
		WHERE Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID = @MaxAdvertlistchangelogID

		--"T�rt�nt-e m�dos�t�s?" vizsg�lat
		IF
			ISNULL(@Title,'') <> ISNULL(@Title_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Description,'') <> ISNULL(@Description_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Categories,'') <> ISNULL(@Categories_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@CompanyID ,'') <> ISNULL(@CompanyID_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Department,'') <> ISNULL(@Department_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Requirements,'') <> ISNULL(@Requirements_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Qualities,'') <> ISNULL(@Qualities_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Benefits,'') <> ISNULL(@Benefits_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Link,'') <> ISNULL(@Link_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Expiraton_Date,'') <> ISNULL(@Expiraton_Date_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Contract,'') <> ISNULL(@Contract_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Schedule,'') <> ISNULL(@Schedule_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Vacancy_NR,'') <> ISNULL(@Vacancy_NR_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Work_Location,'') <> ISNULL(@Work_Location_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Tasks,'') <> ISNULL(@Tasks_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Additional_Info,'') <> ISNULL(@Additional_Info_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Recruiter_Info,'') <> ISNULL(@Recruiter_Info_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Recruiter_ID,'') <> ISNULL(@Recruiter_id_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Recruiter_email,'') <> ISNULL(@Recruiter_Email_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Recruiter_Felvado,'') <> ISNULL(@Recruiter_Felvado_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Map_Job,'') <> ISNULL(@Map_Job_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@CV,'') <> ISNULL(@CV_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Industry,'') <> ISNULL(@Industry_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Hierarchy_Level,'') <> ISNULL(@Hierarchy_Level_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Education_Type,'') <> ISNULL(@Education_Type_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Education_Field,'') <> ISNULL(@Education_Field_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Field_Of_Study,'') <> ISNULL(@Field_Of_Study_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Reference_Number,'') <> ISNULL(@Reference_Number_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Approval_Date,'') <> ISNULL(@Approval_Date_log,'') OR
			ISNULL(@Number_Of_Positions,'') <> ISNULL(@Number_Of_Positions_log,'')
			OR NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM dbo.msk_kex_advertlistchangelog WHERE AdvertID=@AdvertID)
		BEGIN
			INSERT INTO dbo.msk_kex_advertlistchangelog (AdvertListID, Deleted) VALUES (0, 0)

			DECLARE @Uj_msk_kex_advertlistchangelogID INT
			SET @Uj_msk_kex_advertlistchangelogID = SCOPE_IDENTITY()

			UPDATE dbo.msk_kex_advertlistchangelog SET
				AdvertListID = (@Uj_msk_kex_advertlistchangelogID + 4000000),
				AdvertID = @AdvertID,
				Company = @Company,
				Title = @Title,
				Description = @Description,
				Locations = @Locations,
				Categories = @Categories,
				CompanyID = @CompanyID,
				Department = @Department,
				Requirements = @Requirements,
				Qualities = @Qualities,
				Benefits = @Benefits,
				Min_Experience = @Min_Experience,
				Min_Education = @Min_Education,
				Driver_Licence = @Driver_Licence,
				Link = @Link,
				Activation_Date = @Activation_Date,
				Expiraton_Date = @Expiraton_Date,
				Contract = @Contract,
				Schedule = @Schedule,
				Company_Name = @Company_Name,
				Email = @Email,
				Phone = @Phone,
				Vacancy_NR = @Vacancy_NR,
				Work_Location = @Work_Location,
				Hide_Company = @Hide_Company,
				Schow_Apply_Button = @Schow_Apply_Button,
				Custom_Template_ID = @Custom_Template_ID,
				Tasks = @Tasks,
				Additional_Info = @Additional_Info,
				Recruiter_Info = @Recruiter_Info,
				Recruiter_ID = @Recruiter_ID,
				Recruiter_Email = @Recruiter_email,
				Recruiter_Felvado = @Recruiter_Felvado,
				Map_Job = @Map_Job,
				CV = @CV,
				Subsidiary = @Subsidiary,
				Industry = @Industry,
				Hierarchy_Level = @Hierarchy_Level,
				Education_Type = @Education_Type,
				Education_Field = @Education_Field,
				Field_Of_Study = @Field_Of_Study,
				Reference_Number = @Reference_Number,
				Approval_Date = @Approval_Date,
				Number_Of_Positions = @Number_Of_Positions,
				Created = GETDATE()
			WHERE Msk_Kex_AdvertlistchangelogID = @Uj_msk_kex_advertlistchangelogID
		END

END

	DECLARE @AdvertLZCursor CURSOR
	DECLARE @AllasID INT

		BEGIN
			SET @AdvertLZCursor = CURSOR FOR
			SELECT Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek WHERE Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID >= 60000000

				OPEN @AdvertLZCursor 
				FETCH NEXT FROM @AdvertLZCursor 
				INTO @AllasID

				WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0
				BEGIN

				  EXEC [dbo].[msk_tob_msk_kex_advertlistchangelog_frissites] @AllasID

				  FETCH NEXT FROM @AdvertLZCursor
				  INTO @AllasID
				END; 

				CLOSE @AdvertLZCursor;
				DEALLOCATE @AdvertLZCursor;
			END;
PRINT 'TOB POSTD Ended'

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_selenium.sql =====

-- =============================================
-- Author:		Horv�th G�bor
-- Create date: 2022.05.16
-- Description:	Selenium teszt
-- =============================================
CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_selenium] @mode varchar(10), @servername varchar(100)
AS
BEGIN 
	declare @s varchar(50) = concat('Selenium ',@mode)
	declare @s2 varchar(200)
	exec dbo.msk_kki_log_insert @s,''

	if @servername='localhost/effector68' begin

		delete from [dbo].[msk_kex_interju]
		delete from [dbo].[msk_kex_jelentkezok]
		delete from [dbo].[msk_kex_allasajanlatok]
		delete from msk_tob_allashirdetesek
		delete from dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem

		set @s2 = concat('T�bl�k teszthez ki�r�tve: ' , @servername)
		exec dbo.msk_kki_log_insert @s,@s2
	end

END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_setma.sql =====

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_setma]
	@dt datetime 
AS
begin
	IF not EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM dbo.FSYS_ApplicationSetup WHERE code = 'TOB_GETMA')
		INSERT INTO dbo.FSYS_ApplicationSetup (Codevalue,CODE,DELETED) VALUES ('','TOB_GETMA',0)
	if @dt is null
		UPDATE dbo.FSYS_ApplicationSetup SET Deleted=1 WHERE CODE='TOB_GETMA'
	else
		UPDATE dbo.FSYS_ApplicationSetup SET Deleted=0, CodeValue=FORMAT (@dt, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') WHERE CODE='TOB_GETMA'
	RETURN 0
end

/* .........................................
TEST 
Az al�bbi r�szlet be�ll�tja konkr�t d�tumra majd vissza az aktu�lisra a d�tumot.
Az id�pont r�szlet mindig a napi aktu�lis id�t mutatja csak a d�tum �ll �t

EXEC dbo.msk_tob_setma '2022-12-12 12:12:00'
SELECT dbo.msk_tob_getma()
EXEC dbo.msk_tob_setma null
SELECT dbo.msk_tob_getma()

*/

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_spkkmasolas] (@ID int)
AS BEGIN  
	SET NOCOUNT ON  
	  
	SELECT [Msk_tob_keresesikerelemmasolasID] as [type]
		  ,[Megnevezes] as [FragmentCaption] 
	  FROM msk_tob_keresesikerelemmasolas
END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_STA_dll_select.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_STA_DLL_select]	
AS
BEGIN
select (
select PID as "@ID",
ISNULL(case when ltrim(PCOMPANY)='' then '-' else PCOMPANY END,'') as company,
ISNULL(PTITLE,'') as title, 
ISNULL(PDESCRIPTION,'') as description, 
ISNULL(plocation,'') as 'locations/location', 
ISNULL(pcategory,'') as 'categories/category',
ISNULL(PcompanyID,'') as companyID, 
ISNULL(pdepartment,'') as department, 
ISNULL(prequirements,'') as requirements, 
ISNULL(pqualities,'') as qualities, 
ISNULL(pbenefits,'') as benefits, 
ISNULL(pminexperience,'') as min_experience, 
ISNULL(pmineducation,'') as min_education, 
ISNULL(pdriverlicence,'') as driver_license,
ISNULL(plink,'') as link, 
ISNULL(pactivationdate,'') as activation_date, 
ISNULL(pexpirationdate,'') as expiration_date, 
ISNULL(pcontract,'') as contract, 
ISNULL(pschedule,'') as schedule, 
ISNULL(pcompanyname,'') as company_name, 
ISNULL(pemail,'') as email, 
ISNULL(pphone,'') as phone, 
ISNULL(PVACANCYNUMBER,'') as vacancy_nr, 
ISNULL(pworklocation,'') as work_location, 
'false' as hide_company, 
'false' as show_apply_button, 
ISNULL(pcustomtemplateID,'') as custom_template_ID, 
ISNULL(ptasks,'') as tasks, 
ISNULL(padditionalinfo,'') as additional_info, 
ISNULL(precruiterinfo,'') as recruiter_info, 
ISNULL(pfenykepurl,'') as fenykepurl,
ISNULL(pvideourl,'') as videourl,
ISNULL(pproperties,'') as properties
from msk_tob_STA /* where padditionalinfo is not null and padditionalinfo<>'' */
for xml path('advert'), root('WebAdverts')
) as xml
end

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msk_tob_STA_DLL_select_OLD_eredeti.sql =====


CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_STA_DLL_select_OLD_eredeti]	
AS 
BEGIN
select (
 SELECT 'karier@mav.hu' as '@email',
(SELECT TOP (1000) 
	   ISNULL([PITEMID],'') as '@itemId'
      ,ISNULL([PREFID],'') as '@refId'
      ,ISNULL([PCONTACTNAME],'') as '@contactName'
      ,ISNULL([PCONTACTPHONE],'') as '@contactPhone'
      ,ISNULL([PTITLE],'') as 'allast_kinal/title' 
      ,ISNULL([PDESCRIPTION],'') as 'allast_kinal/description'
      ,ISNULL([PREGIO],'') as 'allast_kinal/regio'
      ,ISNULL([PAR],'') as 'allast_kinal/ar'
      ,ISNULL([PIMAGE],'') as 'allast_kinal/images/image'
      ,ISNULL([PURL],'') as 'allast_kinal/url'
      ,ISNULL([PCEGNEV_SZEKTOR],'') as 'allast_kinal/cegnev_szektor'
      ,ISNULL([PPOZICIO],'') as 'allast_kinal/pozicio'
      ,ISNULL([PORIENTACIO],'') as 'allast_kinal/orientacio'
      ,ISNULL([PMUNKAVEGZES_HELYE],'') as 'allast_kinal/munkavegzes_helye'
      ,ISNULL([PISKOLAI_VEGZETTSEG],'') as 'allast_kinal/iskolai_vegzettseg'
      ,ISNULL([PNYELVTUDAS],'') as 'allast_kinal/nyelvtudas'
      ,ISNULL([PJELENTKEZESI_HATARIDO],'') as 'allast_kinal/jelentkezesi_hatarido'
      ,ISNULL([PFOGLALKOZTATAS_MODJA],'') as 'allast_kinal/foglalkoztatas_modja'
      ,ISNULL([PMUNKAIDO],'') as 'allast_kinal/munkaido'
      ,ISNULL([PFIZETESI_SZINT],'') as 'allast_kinal/fizetesi_szint'
--      ,[PSPECIALIS_JELLEG] as 'allast_kinal/specialis_jelleg'
	  from msk_tob_STA_OLD_eredeti as item
FOR XML PATH ('item'), type  ) 
FOR XML PATH ('import')
) as xml



END

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msk_tob_STA_item] 
@ID int
AS
BEGIN
	update msk_tob_allashirdetesek set StatuszSTA=1 where Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID = @ID


	insert into msk_log (name,value,created) values ('STA Interf�sz ITEM OK',@ID,getdate())
	select 'True'
END

		(   @CimzettID, -- Idvezeto - int
			@KKID, -- idallasajanlat - int
			@IsMjgy, -- Mjgy - int
			0, -- Deleted - tinyint
			@IsStatuszolo  -- Statuszolovezeto - tinyint
	    )
	ELSE
		UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok	SET Statuszolovezeto = @IsStatuszolo WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID=@KKVezetoID

	--SELECT '�rtes�t� email sikeresen kik�ldve ' + @Cimzett_neve + ' r�sz�re'

END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msp_tob_getIktatoszam.sql =====

/*
    Created by: Gabor Horvath 2024.01.29 
    TOB Iktat�sz�m gener�tor. 
    Visszad: Utolj�ra gener�lt iktat�sz�m 
    
M�k�d�s:

Ellen�rzi, hogy az Idkeresesikerelem m�r l�tezik-e a msk_tob_headpozicio t�bl�ban. Ha igen, meghat�rozza a Poziciotipus-t 
�s kiv�lasztja a m�r megl�v� iktat�sz�m v�llalatnev�t. Ha nem, akkor be�ll�t egy jelz�t (@ujhead) az �j head rekord l�trehoz�s�ra.
Ellen�rzi, hogy az Idkeresesikerelem m�r l�tezik-e a msk_tob_pozicio t�bl�ban. Ha nem, akkor gener�l egy �j sorsz�mot. 
Ha igen, akkor csak n�veli az alsz�mot.
Besz�r rekordokat az msk_tob_pozicio t�bl�ba a @tanfolyamos �s @mennyiseg param�terek alapj�n:
- Ha a rekord tanfolyamos (@tanfolyamos = 1), akkor @mennyiseg darabsz�m� rekordot sz�r be, minden egyes rekordhoz n�velve az alsz�mot.
- Ha a rekord nem tanfolyamos (@tanfolyamos = 0), akkor csak egy rekordot sz�r be, figyelmen k�v�l hagyva a @mennyiseg param�ter �rt�k�t.
Ha sz�ks�ges, l�trehoz egy �j rekordot a msk_tob_headpozicio t�bl�ban, vagy friss�ti a megl�v� rekord iktat�sz�m�t.
    
*/
CREATE PROCEDURE dbo.msp_tob_getIktatoszam 
    @Idkeresesikerelem INT, 
    @VallalatRovidNeve VARCHAR(50), 
    @tanfolyamos BIT, 
    @mennyiseg INT,
    @datum date,
    @PozicioInfo varchar(50)
AS
BEGIN
    SET NOCOUNT ON;

    DECLARE @Ev INT = YEAR(dbo.msk_tob_getma());
    DECLARE @UjIktatoszam VARCHAR(100);
    DECLARE @MaxSorszam INT;
    DECLARE @Alszam INT;
    DECLARE @PozicioTipus INT;
    DECLARE @IsVanHeadPozicio BIT;
    DECLARE @IsVanPozicio BIT;
    DECLARE @LegutolsoIktatoszam VARCHAR(100);
	DECLARE @AktualisVallalatNeve VARCHAR(50);
	DECLARE @ujhead INT =0
    DECLARE @HeadIktatoszam VARCHAR(100);
    DECLARE @ElsodlegesEngedelyezesiDatum DATE;

insert into msk_log (name,value,created) values ('msp_tob_getIktatoszam1',concat(isnull(@Idkeresesikerelem,'-'),'|',isnull(@VallalatRovidNeve,'-'),'|',isnull(@tanfolyamos,'-'),'|',isnull(@mennyiseg,'-'),'|',isnull(cast(@datum as varchar(20)),'-'),'|',isnull(@PozicioInfo,'-')),getdate())

    -- Ellen�rz�s, hogy l�tezik-e m�r a keres�si k�relem
    SELECT @IsVanHeadPozicio             = CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
		  ,@LegutolsoIktatoszam          = MAX(Iktatoszam)
          ,@ElsodlegesEngedelyezesiDatum = MIN(Engedelyezesidatum)
    FROM msk_tob_headpozicio
    WHERE ( Idkeresesikerelem = @Idkeresesikerelem ) AND DELETED<2

    -- Ugyanolyan jelleg� iktat�sz�m lehet m�sfel� is ha m�solt


    -- @PozicioTipus,@VallalatRovidNeve,@tanfolyamos
    IF @IsVanHeadPozicio = 1
    BEGIN
        SELECT @PozicioTipus = Poziciotipus
        FROM msk_tob_headpozicio
        WHERE ( Idkeresesikerelem = @Idkeresesikerelem or Idkeresesikerelem in (Select distinct AutomataKKID from msk_tob_headpozicio where deleted=0 AND AutomataKKID=@Idkeresesikerelem)) AND DELETED<2		
        SET @VallalatRovidNeve = LEFT(@LegutolsoIktatoszam, CHARINDEX('-', @LegutolsoIktatoszam) - 1);
        SET @tanfolyamos = CASE WHEN @PozicioTipus = 41 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END;
    END
    ELSE
    BEGIN
        SET @PozicioTipus = CASE WHEN @tanfolyamos = 1 THEN 41 ELSE 40 END;
		SET @ujhead = 1
    END

    -- Ellen�rz�s, hogy van-e m�r bejegyz�s a pozicio t�bl�ban
    SELECT @IsVanPozicio = CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM msk_tob_pozicio WHERE Idkeresesikerelem = @Idkeresesikerelem AND DELETED<2    
    SELECT @LegutolsoIktatoszam = MAX(Iktatoszam) FROM msk_tob_pozicio WHERE left(iktatoszam,14)=left(@LegutolsoIktatoszam,14) AND DELETED<2		

insert into msk_log (name,value,created) values ('msp_tob_getIktatoszam2',concat(isnull(@tanfolyamos,'-'),'|',isnull(@mennyiseg,'-'),'|',isnull(cast(@datum as varchar(20)),'-'),'|',isnull(@PozicioInfo,'-')),getdate())
insert into msk_log (name,value,created) values ('msp_tob_getIktatoszam3',concat(isnull(@IsVanHeadPozicio,'-'),'|',isnull(@LegutolsoIktatoszam,'-'),'|',isnull(cast(@ElsodlegesEngedelyezesiDatum as varchar(20)),'-'),'|',isnull(@IsVanPozicio,'-')),getdate())

    IF @IsVanPozicio = 0
    BEGIN
        -- �j sorsz�m gener�l�sa az aktu�lis �vvel
        SELECT @MaxSorszam = ISNULL(MAX(CONVERT(INT, SUBSTRING(Iktatoszam, CHARINDEX('-', Iktatoszam) + 1, 4))), 0) + 1
        FROM msk_tob_pozicio
        WHERE Iktatoszam LIKE @VallalatRovidNeve + '-%' AND Iktatoszam LIKE '%/' + CAST(@Ev AS VARCHAR) + '/%' AND DELETED<2;
        SET @Alszam = 1;
    END
    ELSE
    BEGIN
        -- Alsz�m n�vel�se, de az iktat�sz�m �vsz�m�t megtartjuk
        SET @MaxSorszam = CONVERT(INT, SUBSTRING(@LegutolsoIktatoszam, CHARINDEX('-', @LegutolsoIktatoszam) + 1, 4));
        SET @Alszam = CONVERT(INT, RIGHT(@LegutolsoIktatoszam, 3)) + 1;
        SET @Ev = CONVERT(INT, SUBSTRING(@LegutolsoIktatoszam, CHARINDEX('/', @LegutolsoIktatoszam) + 1, 4)); -- Az iktat�sz�m �vsz�m�nak kinyer�se
    END

    SET @UjIktatoszam = @VallalatRovidNeve + '-' + RIGHT('0000' + CAST(@MaxSorszam AS VARCHAR), 4) + '/' + CAST(@Ev AS VARCHAR) + '/' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(@Alszam AS VARCHAR), 3);
	SET @headiktatoszam = @UjIktatoszam
    -- Besz�r�s az msk_tob_pozicio t�bl�ba
insert into msk_log (name,value,created) values ('msp_tob_getIktatoszam4',concat(isnull(@UjIktatoszam,'-'),'|',isnull(@headiktatoszam,'-'),'|',isnull(@MaxSorszam,'-'),'|',isnull(@Alszam,'-'),'|',isnull(@ujhead,'-')),getdate())

    IF @tanfolyamos = 1
    BEGIN
        if @IsVanPozicio = 1 begin
            SET @datum = ISNULL(@ElsodlegesEngedelyezesiDatum, @datum); 
        end

        if @mennyiseg>0 begin
            if @mennyiseg>99 begin
                set @mennyiseg=99
            end
            DECLARE @i INT = 1;
            WHILE @i <= @mennyiseg
            BEGIN
                INSERT INTO msk_tob_pozicio (Idkeresesikerelem, Iktatoszam, Aliktatoszam, Engedelyezesidatum, StatuszID, Deleted,PozicioInfo)
                VALUES (@Idkeresesikerelem, @UjIktatoszam, @Alszam, @datum, 32, 0,@PozicioInfo);
			    SET @headiktatoszam = @UjIktatoszam
                SET @Alszam = @Alszam + 1;
                SET @UjIktatoszam = @VallalatRovidNeve + '-' + RIGHT('0000' + CAST(@MaxSorszam AS VARCHAR), 4) + '/' + CAST(@Ev AS VARCHAR) + '/' + RIGHT('000' + CAST(@Alszam AS VARCHAR), 3);
                SET @i = @i + 1;
            END
        end
    END
    ELSE
    BEGIN
        INSERT INTO msk_tob_pozicio (Idkeresesikerelem, Iktatoszam, Aliktatoszam, Engedelyezesidatum, StatuszID, Deleted,PozicioInfo)
        VALUES (@Idkeresesikerelem, @UjIktatoszam, @Alszam, @datum, 32, 0,@PozicioInfo);
    END

    -- �j rekord a headpozicio t�bl�ba
	IF @ujhead=1 BEGIN
        INSERT INTO msk_tob_headpozicio (Idkeresesikerelem, Poziciotipus, Iktatoszam, Engedelyezesidatum, Deleted)
        VALUES (@Idkeresesikerelem, @PozicioTipus, @HeadIktatoszam, @datum, 0);
    END ELSE BEGIN
		UPDATE msk_tob_headpozicio SET Iktatoszam = @HeadIktatoszam WHERE Idkeresesikerelem = @Idkeresesikerelem;
	END

	--SELECT @HeadIktatoszam
END
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Stored Procedures\msp_tob_tomeges_portalallashirdetes.sql =====

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[msp_tob_tomeges_portalallashirdetes]
AS 
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON
	

	SELECT Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID FROM dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek
	WHERE Pubcsoportportal=1 AND Datum_lejarat > GETDATE()

END

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Tables\msk_tob_allashirdetesek.sql =====

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[msk_tob_allashirdetesek] (
    [Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID] INT            IDENTITY (60000001, 1) NOT NULL,
    [Idkeresesikerelem]         INT            NULL,
    [Targy]                     VARCHAR (255)  NULL,
    [StatuszID]                 INT            NULL,
    [Datum_lejarat]             DATE           NULL,
    [CsatolmanyID]              INT            NULL,
    [Fejlecszoveg]              VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Feladatok]                 VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Tulajdonsagok]             VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Elvarasok]                 VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Elonytjelent]              VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Juttatasok]                VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Tovabbi_info]              VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Toborzo_info]              VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Toborzonev]                VARCHAR (250)  NULL,
    [Toborzotelefonszam]        VARCHAR (50)   NULL,
    [Vallalatibemutatkozo]      VARCHAR (MAX)  NULL,
    [Datum_jovahagyas]          DATE           NULL,
    [Datum_publikalas]          DATE           NULL,
    [Link]                      VARCHAR (2000) NULL,
    [Datum_lezaras]             DATE           NULL,
    [VegzettsegiszintID]        INT            NULL,
    [Pubcsoportportal]          BIT            NULL,
    [PubCVO]                    BIT            NULL,
    [PubSTA]                    BIT            NULL,
    [FenykepURL]                VARCHAR (1000) NULL,
    [VideoURL]                  VARCHAR (1000) NULL,
    [Deleted]                   TINYINT        NULL,
    [LetrehozoID]               INT            NULL,
    [StatuszCSP]                TINYINT        NULL,
    [StatuszCVO]                TINYINT        NULL,
    [StatuszSTA]                TINYINT        NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID] ASC)
);




















GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem] (
    [Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID] INT           IDENTITY (1, 1) NOT NULL,
    [Cim]                       VARCHAR (250) NULL,
    [StatuszID]                 INT           NULL,
    [Iktatoszam]                VARCHAR (50)  NULL,
    [Engedelyezesidatum]        DATE          NULL,
    [Munkakor]                  VARCHAR (250) NULL,
    [Lejaratidatum]             DATE          NULL,
    [Pozicioszam]               INT           NULL,
    [TeruletiigazgatosagID]     INT           NULL,
    [SzakteruletID]             INT           NULL,
    [SzervezetiegyesegID]       INT           NULL,
    [SzerzodesfajtaID]          INT           NULL,
    [MunkavegzeshelyeID]        INT           NULL,
    [Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb]     VARCHAR (250) NULL,
    [Cv]                        TINYINT       NULL,
    [MunkakorcsoportID]         INT           NULL,
    [FoglalkoztatasifokID]      INT           NULL,
    [Kepzes_fajtaID]            INT           NULL,
    [Kepzes_szakiranyID]        INT           NULL,
    [MMKkod]                    INT           NULL,
    [Berlatszik]                TINYINT       NULL,
    [Berkotelezo]               TINYINT       NULL,
    [Map_job]                   TINYINT       NULL,
    [Idtoborzo1]                INT           NULL,
    [Idtoborzo2]                INT           NULL,
    [Idengedelyezo]             INT           NULL,
    [Idceg]                     INT           NULL,
    [Deleted]                   TINYINT       NULL,
    [Szerzodes_befejezes]       DATE          NULL,
    [Lezaras]                   BIT           NULL,
    [Created]                   DATETIME      DEFAULT (getdate()) NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID] ASC) WITH (FILLFACTOR = 80)
);












GO
-- =============================================
-- Author:		Najdanovszki Kriszti�n	
-- Create date: 2019.10.03.
-- Description:	Keres�si k�relem lez�r�sa false est�n t�r�lje a lez�r�s indoka mez�t
-- =============================================
CREATE TRIGGER keresesikerelem_update
   ON  dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem
   AFTER UPDATE
AS 
BEGIN
	-- SET NOCOUNT ON added to prevent extra result sets from
	-- interfering with SELECT statements.
	SET NOCOUNT ON;
	
	UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem SET StatuszID = NULL WHERE Lezaras = 'false'

END
GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem(SzakteruletID,Deleted)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]([SzakteruletID] ASC, [Deleted] ASC);


GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem(StatuszID,Deleted)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]([StatuszID] ASC, [Deleted] ASC);


GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem(Idengedelyezo,Deleted)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]([Idengedelyezo] ASC, [Deleted] ASC);


GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem(Idceg,Deleted)_INCLUDE(Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID,Cim,StatuszID,Iktatoszam,)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]([Idceg] ASC, [Deleted] ASC)
    INCLUDE([Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID], [Cim], [StatuszID], [Iktatoszam], [Map_job], [Idtoborzo1], [Idtoborzo2], [Idengedelyezo], [Szerzodes_befejezes], [Lezaras], [FoglalkoztatasifokID], [Kepzes_fajtaID], [Kepzes_szakiranyID], [MMKkod], [Berlatszik], [Berkotelezo], [SzervezetiegyesegID], [SzerzodesfajtaID], [MunkavegzeshelyeID], [Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb], [Cv], [MunkakorcsoportID], [Engedelyezesidatum], [Munkakor], [Lejaratidatum], [Pozicioszam], [TeruletiigazgatosagID], [SzakteruletID]);



GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem(Deleted)_INCLUDE(Idtoborzo1)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]([Deleted] ASC)
    INCLUDE([Idtoborzo1], [Idtoborzo2]);


GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem(Created)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem]([Created] ASC);

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok] (
    [Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID] INT     IDENTITY (1, 1) NOT NULL,
    [Idvezeto]                          INT     NULL,
    [Idkeresesikerelem]                 INT     NULL,
    [Mjgy]                              INT     NULL,
    [Deleted]                           TINYINT NULL,
    [Statuszolovezeto]                  BIT NULL,
    PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED ([Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID] ASC)

GO

    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok] ( [Idvezeto], [Idkeresesikerelem], [Mjgy], [Deleted] )
    INCLUDE ( [Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID] )
GO

CREATE INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok(Idkeresesikerelem,Deleted,Statuszolovezeto)_INCLUDE(Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok] ( [Idkeresesikerelem], [Deleted], [Statuszolovezeto] )
    INCLUDE ( [Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID] )
GO

CREATE INDEX [IX_msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok(Idkeresesikerelem,Deleted)_INCLUDE(Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID)]
    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok] ( [Idkeresesikerelem], [Deleted] )
    INCLUDE ( [Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID] )
GO

-- =============================================
-- Author:		<Author,,Name>
-- Create date: <Create Date,,>
-- Description:	<Description,,>
-- =============================================
CREATE TRIGGER [dbo].[VezetoNullazo]
   ON  [dbo].[msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok]
   AFTER UPDATE, INSERT
AS 
BEGIN
	-- Ha a t�r�lt vezet� egybe STvezet� is akkor null�za az idvezet�t
	SET NOCOUNT ON;
	DECLARE @newAZ int;
	DECLARE @newIdvezeto int;
	DECLARE @newIDKK int;
	DECLARE @newMjgy int;
	DECLARE @newStatuszolovezeto TINYINT;
	DECLARE @newDeleted int;
	DECLARE @MJGYtsz varchar(10);
	SELECT 
	@newAZ= Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID, 
	@newIdvezeto = Idvezeto, 
	@newIDKK = Idkeresesikerelem,
	@newMjgy = Mjgy,
	@newStatuszolovezeto = Statuszolovezeto,
	@newDeleted=Deleted 
	FROM inserted

	IF @newStatuszolovezeto = 1
	BEGIN
	  UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok
	  SET Statuszolovezeto = 0
	  WHERE Idkeresesikerelem = @newIDKK AND NOT idvezeto = @newIdvezeto
	END

	IF @newStatuszolovezeto = 0
	BEGIN
	  UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok
	  SET Statuszolovezeto = 0
	  WHERE Msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetokID=@newAZ
	END

	INSERT dbo.msk_log
	(
	    name,
	    value,
	    created
	)
	VALUES
	(   'statuszol�',           -- name - varchar(100)
	    @newStatuszolovezeto,           -- value - varchar(max)
	    SYSDATETIME() -- created - datetime2(7)
	    )


	IF @newDeleted = 1 
	BEGIN
		-- Ha a t�r�lt vezet� egybe STvezet� is akkor null�za az idvezet�t
--		IF @newMjgy = 9  
--		BEGIN
--			UPDATE msk_kex_allasajanlatok SET idvezeto = NULL  WHERE msk_kex_allasajanlatokID = @newIdallasajanlat AND idvezeto = @newIdvezeto
--		END
		-- Ha a t�r�lt vezet� munk�ltat�jogk�r gyakorl� akkor t�rli a fi� vezet�ket
		IF @newMjgy = 10 
		BEGIN
			SELECT @MJGYtsz = PERNR FROM People WHERE Deleted = 0 AND PeopleID = @newIdvezeto
			UPDATE dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem_vezetok SET Deleted = 1  
			WHERE Idkeresesikerelem = @newIDKK AND Idvezeto in (SELECT PeopleID FROM People WHERE PSTLZ=@MJGYtsz)
		END
	END
END

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[msk_tob_pozicio] (
[PozicioID] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL,
[Idkeresesikerelem] [int] NULL,
[Iktatoszam] [varchar](100) NULL,
[Aliktatoszam] [varchar](100) NULL,
[Engedelyezesidatum] [date] NULL,
[StatuszID] [int] NULL,
[Deleted] [tinyint] NULL, 
[Pre_Torles] INT NULL, 
[TorlesindokID] INT NULL,
[PozicioInfo] [varchar](50) NULL,
[PozicioVisszavDatum] [date] NULL
);

GO

    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_pozicio]([Iktatoszam] ASC, [Deleted] ASC);

GO

    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_pozicio]([Idkeresesikerelem] ASC, [StatuszID] ASC, [Deleted] ASC)
    INCLUDE([PozicioID], [Engedelyezesidatum]);

GO

    ON [dbo].[msk_tob_pozicio]([Idkeresesikerelem] ASC, [StatuszID] ASC, [Deleted] ASC);

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_tob_CVO.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_tob_CVO
AS
SELECT        dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatusz.Keresesikerelemstatusz, dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet.CVOextID AS PCATEGORY, dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok.CVOextID AS PSCHEDULE, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta.CVOextID AS PMINEDUCATION, kk.Pozicioszam AS PVACANCYNUMBER, kk.Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb AS PWORKLOCATION, kk.Cv, kk.Idceg AS PCOMPANYID, ah.Targy AS PTITLE, 
                         ah.Feladatok AS PTASKS, ah.Elvarasok AS PREQUIREMENTS, ah.Elonytjelent AS PQUALITIES, ah.Juttatasok AS PBENEFITS, ah.Fejlecszoveg AS PADDITIONALINFO, 
                         ah.Toborzo_info AS PEMAIL, { fn CONCAT({ fn CONCAT(ah.Toborzonev, ' ') }, ah.Toborzotelefonszam) } AS PRECRUITERINFO, ah.Vallalatibemutatkozo AS PDESCRIPTION, ah.Link AS PLINK, ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID AS PID, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek.Telepules AS PLOCATION, ah.Datum_publikalas AS PACTIVATIONDATE, dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta.Szerzodesfajta AS PCONTRACT, ah.Datum_lejarat AS PEXPIRATIONDATE, 
                         dbo.orn_SZI_Company.Name AS PCOMPANYNAME, 0 AS PHIDECOMPANY, 0 AS PSHOWAPPLYBUTTON, dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras.CVOextID AS PCUSTOMTEMPLATEID, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok.Igazgatosagok AS PDEPARTMENT, kk.Deleted, ah.Toborzotelefonszam AS PPHONE, dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID AS Hirdetesstatusz, kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID, 
                         232 AS PMINEXPERIENCE, 0 AS PDRIVERLICENCE, dbo.orn_SZI_Company.Name AS PCOMPANY, ah.FenykepURL AS PFENYKEPURL, ah.VideoURL AS PVIDEOURL, ah.Tulajdonsagok AS PPROPERTIES
FROM            dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras RIGHT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem AS kk ON dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras.Idceg = kk.Idceg LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.orn_SZI_Company ON kk.Idceg = dbo.orn_SZI_Company.AllasVallalatKod LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet ON kk.SzakteruletID = dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet.Msk_tob_szakteruletID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesjelleg ON kk.Kepzes_szakiranyID = dbo.msk_tob_kepzesjelleg.Msk_tob_kepzesjellegID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta ON kk.Kepzes_fajtaID = dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta.Msk_tob_kepzesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok ON kk.FoglalkoztatasifokID = dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok.Msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifokID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_munkakoricsoport ON kk.MunkakorcsoportID = dbo.msk_tob_munkakoricsoport.Msk_tob_munkakoricsoportID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek ON kk.MunkavegzeshelyeID = dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek.Msk_tob_telepulesekID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta ON kk.SzerzodesfajtaID = dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta.Msk_tob_szerzodesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek AS ah LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint ON ah.VegzettsegiszintID = dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint.Msk_tob_vegzettsegiszintID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_LookupList ON ah.StatuszID = dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = ah.Idkeresesikerelem LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatusz ON kk.StatuszID = dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatusz.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatuszID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok ON kk.TeruletiigazgatosagID = dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok.Msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagokID
WHERE        (kk.Deleted = 0) AND (ah.Deleted = 0) AND (ah.Pubcsoportportal = 1) AND (dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID = 22) AND (ah.Datum_lejarat >= GETDATE()) AND (ah.StatuszCSP = 1) AND (ah.PubCVO = 1)
GO
EXECUTE sp_addextendedproperty @name = N'MS_DiagramPaneCount', @value = 2, @level0type = N'SCHEMA', @level0name = N'dbo', @level1type = N'VIEW', @level1name = N'msk_tob_CVO';


GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_tob_portalallashirdetes.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_tob_portalallashirdetes
AS
SELECT        ISNULL(1, '') AS EntitasVerzio, ISNULL(ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID, '') AS id, ISNULL(c.Name, '') AS company, ISNULL(ah.Targy, '') AS title, ISNULL(kk.Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb, ISNULL(t.Telepules, '')) AS location, 
                         ISNULL(szt.CSPextID, '') AS category, ISNULL(kk.Idceg, '') AS companyid, ISNULL(kk.SzervezetiegyesegID, '') AS department, ISNULL(ah.Elvarasok, '') AS requirements, ISNULL(ah.Elonytjelent, '') AS qualities, 
                         ISNULL(ah.Juttatasok, '') AS benefits, ISNULL(0, '') AS minExperience, ISNULL(0, '') AS minEducation, ISNULL(0, '') AS driverLicense, ISNULL(ah.Datum_publikalas, '') AS activationDate, ISNULL(ah.Datum_lejarat, '') 
                         AS expirationDate, ISNULL(szf.Szerzodesfajta, '') AS contract, ISNULL(0, '') AS companyName, ISNULL(0, '') AS email, ISNULL(0, '') AS phone, ISNULL(kk.Pozicioszam, '') AS vacancyNumber, 
                         ISNULL(kk.Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb, ISNULL(t.Telepules, '')) AS workLocation, ISNULL(0, '') AS hideCompany, ISNULL(0, '') AS showApplyButton, ISNULL(ah.Feladatok, '') AS tasks, ISNULL(ah.Tulajdonsagok, '') AS properties, 
                         ISNULL(ah.Fejlecszoveg, '') AS additionalInfo, { fn CONCAT({ fn CONCAT(ISNULL(ah.Toborzonev, ''), ' ') }, ISNULL(ah.Toborzotelefonszam, '')) } AS recruiterInfo, ISNULL(p.PERNR, '') AS recruiterId, ISNULL(p.Email, '') 
                         AS recruiterEmail, ISNULL(ah.VideoURL, '') AS recruiterFelvado, ISNULL(kk.Map_job, '') AS MAPJob, ISNULL(kk.Cv, '') AS Cv, ISNULL(kk.Berlatszik, '') AS BrBerVisible, ISNULL(kk.Berkotelezo, '') AS BrBerMandatory, ISNULL(0, '') 
                         AS subsidiary, ISNULL(ti.CSPextID, '') AS tiCSPextID, ISNULL(ah.FenykepURL, '') AS fieldsOfStudy, ISNULL(kk.Idtoborzo1, '') AS Idtoborzo1, ISNULL(kk.Idtoborzo2, '') AS Idtoborzo2, ISNULL(kk.Engedelyezesidatum, '') 
                         AS Engedelyezesidatum, ISNULL(kk.Iktatoszam, '') AS Iktatoszam, ISNULL(ah.Deleted, '') AS Deleted, ISNULL(ah.Link, '') AS Link, ISNULL(ff.CSPextID, '') AS schedule, ISNULL(mkcs.CSPextID, '') AS mkcsCSPextID, 
                         ISNULL(kf.CSPextID, '') AS kfCSPextID, ISNULL(kj.CSPextID, '') AS kjCSPextID, ISNULL(ti.Igazgatosagok, '') AS industry, ISNULL(mkcs.CSPextID, '') AS hierarchyLeve, ISNULL(kf.CSPextID, '') AS educationType, 
                         ISNULL(kj.Kepzesjelleg, '') AS educationField, ISNULL(vl.CVOextID, '') AS customTemplateId, ISNULL(vl.Leiras, '') AS description
FROM            dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem AS kk INNER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek AS ah ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = ah.Idkeresesikerelem LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.orn_SZI_Company AS c ON kk.Idceg = c.AllasVallalatKod LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras AS vl ON kk.Idceg = vl.Idceg LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok AS ff ON kk.FoglalkoztatasifokID = ff.Msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifokID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok AS ti ON kk.TeruletiigazgatosagID = ti.Msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagokID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta AS kf ON kk.Kepzes_fajtaID = kf.Msk_tob_kepzesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesjelleg AS kj ON kk.Kepzes_szakiranyID = kj.Msk_tob_kepzesjellegID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.People AS p ON kk.Idtoborzo1 = p.PeopleID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_munkakoricsoport AS mkcs ON kk.MunkakorcsoportID = mkcs.Msk_tob_munkakoricsoportID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta AS szf ON kk.SzerzodesfajtaID = szf.Msk_tob_szerzodesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek AS t ON t.Msk_tob_telepulesekID = kk.MunkavegzeshelyeID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet AS szt ON szt.Msk_tob_szakteruletID = kk.SzakteruletID
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_tob_STA.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_tob_STA
AS
SELECT        dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatusz.Keresesikerelemstatusz, dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet.CVOextID AS PCATEGORY, dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok.CVOextID AS PSCHEDULE, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta.CVOextID AS PMINEDUCATION, kk.Pozicioszam AS PVACANCYNUMBER, kk.Munkavegzeshelyeegyeb AS PWORKLOCATION, kk.Cv, kk.Idceg AS PCOMPANYID, ah.Targy AS PTITLE, 
                         ah.Feladatok AS PTASKS, ah.Elvarasok AS PREQUIREMENTS, ah.Elonytjelent AS PQUALITIES, ah.Juttatasok AS PBENEFITS, ah.Fejlecszoveg AS PADDITIONALINFO, 
                         ah.Toborzo_info AS PEMAIL, { fn CONCAT({ fn CONCAT(ah.Toborzonev, ' ') }, ah.Toborzotelefonszam) } AS PRECRUITERINFO, ah.Vallalatibemutatkozo AS PDESCRIPTION, ah.Link AS PLINK, ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID AS PID, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek.Telepules AS PLOCATION, ah.Datum_publikalas AS PACTIVATIONDATE, dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta.Szerzodesfajta AS PCONTRACT, ah.Datum_lejarat AS PEXPIRATIONDATE, 
                         dbo.orn_SZI_Company.Name AS PCOMPANYNAME, 0 AS PHIDECOMPANY, 0 AS PSHOWAPPLYBUTTON, dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras.CVOextID AS PCUSTOMTEMPLATEID, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok.Igazgatosagok AS PDEPARTMENT, kk.Deleted, ah.Toborzotelefonszam AS PPHONE, dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID AS Hirdetesstatusz, kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID, 
                         232 AS PMINEXPERIENCE, 0 AS PDRIVERLICENCE, dbo.orn_SZI_Company.Name AS PCOMPANY, ah.FenykepURL AS PFENYKEPURL, ah.VideoURL AS PVIDEOURL, ah.Tulajdonsagok AS PPROPERTIES
FROM            dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras RIGHT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem AS kk ON dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras.Idceg = kk.Idceg LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.orn_SZI_Company ON kk.Idceg = dbo.orn_SZI_Company.AllasVallalatKod LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet ON kk.SzakteruletID = dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet.Msk_tob_szakteruletID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesjelleg ON kk.Kepzes_szakiranyID = dbo.msk_tob_kepzesjelleg.Msk_tob_kepzesjellegID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta ON kk.Kepzes_fajtaID = dbo.msk_tob_kepzesfajta.Msk_tob_kepzesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok ON kk.FoglalkoztatasifokID = dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok.Msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifokID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_munkakoricsoport ON kk.MunkakorcsoportID = dbo.msk_tob_munkakoricsoport.Msk_tob_munkakoricsoportID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek ON kk.MunkavegzeshelyeID = dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek.Msk_tob_telepulesekID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta ON kk.SzerzodesfajtaID = dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta.Msk_tob_szerzodesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek AS ah LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint ON ah.VegzettsegiszintID = dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint.Msk_tob_vegzettsegiszintID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_LookupList ON ah.StatuszID = dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = ah.Idkeresesikerelem LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatusz ON kk.StatuszID = dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatusz.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemstatuszID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok ON kk.TeruletiigazgatosagID = dbo.msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagok.Msk_tob_teruletiigazgatosagokID
WHERE        (kk.Deleted = 0) AND (ah.Deleted = 0) AND (ah.Pubcsoportportal = 1) AND (ah.Datum_lejarat >= GETDATE()) AND (ah.StatuszCSP = 1) AND (dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID = 22) AND (ah.PubSTA = 1)
GO
EXECUTE sp_addextendedproperty @name = N'MS_DiagramPaneCount', @value = 3, @level0type = N'SCHEMA', @level0name = N'dbo', @level1type = N'VIEW', @level1name = N'msk_tob_STA';

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_tob_STA_OLD_eredeti.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.[msk_tob_STA_OLD_eredeti]
AS
SELECT        ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID AS PITEMID, vl.STAextID AS PREFID, ah.Toborzonev AS PCONTACTNAME, ah.Toborzotelefonszam AS PCONTACTPHONE, ah.Targy AS PTITLE,
                             (SELECT        { fn CONCAT
                                                             ((SELECT        { fn CONCAT
                                                                                              ((SELECT        { fn CONCAT
                                                                                                                               ((SELECT        { fn CONCAT
                                                                                                                                                                ((SELECT        { fn CONCAT
                                                                                                                                                                                                 ((SELECT        CASE WHEN (ISNULL(aha.Feladatok, '') <> '') THEN (CONCAT('   Feladatok: ', aha.Feladatok)) ELSE (CONCAT('', '')) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                              END AS PDESCRIPTION
                                                                                                                                                                                                     FROM            dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem AS kk LEFT OUTER JOIN
                                                                                                                                                                                                                              dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek AS aha ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = aha.Idkeresesikerelem LEFT OUTER JOIN
                                                                                                                                                                                                                              dbo.msk_tob_LookupList ON aha.StatuszID = dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID
                                                                                                                                                                                                     WHERE        (kk.Deleted = 0) AND (aha.Deleted = 0) AND (aha.Pubcsoportportal = 1) AND (aha.Datum_lejarat >= GETDATE()) AND (aha.PubSTA = 1) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                              AND (dbo.msk_tob_LookupList.LookupListID = 22) AND (aha.StatuszCSP = 1) AND 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                              (aha.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID = ah.Msk_tob_allashirdetesekID)),
                                                                                                                                                                                                 (SELECT        CASE WHEN (ISNULL(aha.Elvarasok, '') <> '') THEN (CONCAT('    Elv�r�sok: ', aha.Elvarasok)) ELSE (CONCAT('', '')) 
                                                                                                                                                                                                                             END AS PDESCRIPTION
                                                                                                                                                                                                   FROM            dbo.msk_tob_keresesikerelem AS kk LEFT OUTER JOIN
                                                                                                                                                                                                                             dbo.msk_tob_allashirdetesek AS aha ON kk.Msk_tob_keresesikerelemID = aha.Idkeresesikerelem LEFT OUTER JOIN

                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek.Telepules AS PMUNKAVEGZES_HELYE, dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint.Vegzettsegiszint AS PISKOLAI_VEGZETTSEG, ' ' AS PNYELVTUDAS, kk.Lejaratidatum AS PJELENTKEZESI_HATARIDO, 
                         dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta.STAextID AS PFOGLALKOZTATAS_MODJA, dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok.STAextID AS PMUNKAIDO, 'versenyk�pes' AS PFIZETESI_SZINT, ' ' AS PSPECIALIS_JELLEG

                         dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek ON kk.MunkavegzeshelyeID = dbo.msk_tob_telepulesek.Msk_tob_telepulesekID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet ON kk.SzakteruletID = dbo.msk_tob_szakterulet.Msk_tob_szakteruletID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.orn_SZI_Company ON kk.Idceg = dbo.orn_SZI_Company.AllasVallalatKod LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint ON ah.VegzettsegiszintID = dbo.msk_tob_vegzettsegiszint.Msk_tob_vegzettsegiszintID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok ON kk.FoglalkoztatasifokID = dbo.msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifok.Msk_tob_foglalkoztatasifokID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta ON kk.SzerzodesfajtaID = dbo.msk_tob_szerzodesfajta.Msk_tob_szerzodesfajtaID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_LookupList AS msk_tob_LookupList_1 ON ah.StatuszID = msk_tob_LookupList_1.LookupListID LEFT OUTER JOIN
                         dbo.msk_tob_vallalatleiras AS vl ON kk.Idceg = vl.Idceg
WHERE        (kk.Deleted = 0) AND (ah.Deleted = 0) AND (ah.Pubcsoportportal = 1) AND (ah.Datum_lejarat >= GETDATE()) AND (ah.PubSTA = 1) AND (msk_tob_LookupList_1.LookupListID = 22) AND (ah.StatuszCSP = 1)
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Views\msk_tob_szervezetiegyseg.sql =====

CREATE VIEW dbo.msk_tob_szervezetiegyseg
AS
SELECT DISTINCT ORGEH AS Kod, ORGTX AS Nev, BUKRS
FROM            dbo.People
WHERE        (Deleted = 0)
GO

===== FILE: C:\hop2\src\Hrportal-Root\HRPortalDB\dbo\Functions\Max2.sql =====

create function Max2(@val1 int, @val2 int)
returns int
as
begin
  if @val1 > @val2
    return @val1
  return isnull(@val2,@val1)
end
